<span data-ttu-id="4312e-165">Te dogodke si lahko ogledate s pregledovalnikom diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-165">You can see these events by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>



## <a name="authentication-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-166">Dogodki preverjanja pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-166">Authentication events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-167">Ti dogodki diagnostičnih podatkov se zberejo, ko Office poskuša pridobiti žeton za preverjanje pristnosti (na tih način ali prek poziva).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-167">These diagnostic data events are collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroidmsaguesttoaad"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-168">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-168">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-169">S tem dogodkom lažje razumemo, kako številni uporabniki med dostopanjem do službenega vira, dobivajo pozive za vnos gesla osebnega računa, saj njihov osebni račun lahko predstavlja veljaven gostujoči račun za najemnika službenih računov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-169">This event helps in understanding how many users are getting prompted for providing personal account password, while accessing work resource, as their personal account could be a valid guest to work account's tenant.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-170">S temi podatki lažje razumemo, kako se morajo številni uporabniki prebiti prek mukotrpnih pozivov za vpis za dodelitev prioritet pri pridobivanju žetona za AAD glede na Microsoftovo izjavo za račun SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-170">This data helps us understand how many users are going through the pain of sign in re-prompts to prioritize AAD token acquisition silently based on a Microsoft account SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) assertion.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-171">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-171">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-172">**Tag** – ponazarja, da je bil uporabniku med dostopanjem do službenega vira prikazan poziv za vpis v osebni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-172">**Tag** - Indicates that user got sign-in prompt for personal account, while accessing work account resource.</span></span>


### <a name="officeidentityfbapromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-173">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-173">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-174">Dogodki se zberejo, ko Office uporabniku prikaže poziv za vpis s preverjanjem pristnosti z obrazci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-174">Collected when Office shows the user a Forms-Based-Auth sign-in prompt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-175">Poleg tihih pridobitev žetonom se s pozivi za preverjanje pristnosti ugotovi, ali je za uporabnika aktivirano stanje prekinjenega preverjanja pristnosti. Uporabnik se tako nahaja v stanju odjemalca brez povezave, v najslabšem primeru pa prekinjeno preverjanje pristnosti lahko povzroči pridobivanje licence in onemogoči odjemalca v celoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-175">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts is used to determine if user is in a broken authentication state which, for the user, results in what is essentially an Offline Client state, or in the worst case, broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-176">Pozivi za vpis s preverjanjem pristnosti z obrazci se uporabljajo za nekatere scenarije preverjanja pristnosti na mestu uporabe, vendar tega običajno ne želimo, ker bi uporabniki morali uporabljati sodobno preverjanje pristnosti zaradi varnostnih ranljivosti, povezanih s preverjanjem pristnosti z obrazci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-176">Forms-Based-Auth (FBA) sign-in prompts are used for some on-premises authentication scenarios and typically we want to make sure this isn't happening, as everyone should be using Modern-Auth because of security vulnerabilities associated with FBA.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-177">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-177">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-178">**AuthScheme** – uporabljena shema za preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-178">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-179">**DocumentUrlHash** – zahteva za šifrirani URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-179">**DocumentUrlHash** - an encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-180">**EndTag** – oznaka, pri kateri se zaključi obrazec za preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-180">**EndTag** - the tag where FBA form is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-181">**Flags** – zastarelo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-181">**Flags** - Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-182">**FlowTag** – oznaka, pri kateri se začne obrazec za preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-182">**FlowTag** - the tag where FBA form is started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-183">**LastError** – vrnjena koda napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-183">**LastError** – the error code returned</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-184">**PromptEndTime** – čas, ko se je poziv končal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-184">**PromptEndTime** - the time when then prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-185">**PromptStartTime** – čas, ko se je poziv začel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-185">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-186">**Result** – ali je bilo preverjanje pristnosti uspešno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-186">**Result** - whether the authentication succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-187">**SessionEndTime** – čas, ko se konča seja dogodka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-187">**SessionEndTime** – the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-188">**Timeout** – čas, ko je potekla časovna omejitev poziva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-188">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt timed out</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysignoutevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-189">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-189">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-190">Dogodki se zberejo, ko se uporabnik izpiše iz Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-190">Collected when a user signs out of Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-191">Če veste, da se je uporabnik izpisal, lahko pričakovano razvrstite druge dogodke, na primer pozive, da bodo ti dogodki lahko pravilno izračunani v metriki zanesljivosti/pripravljenosti na odpremo. Prav tako se lahko izognete opozorilom oziroma razveljavljanju gradenj ob lažni predpostavki, da je uporabnik deležen nepričakovanih pozivov za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-191">Knowing the user is signed-out makes it possible to classify other events, such as prompts, as expected, so those events can be correctly computed in reliability / ship-readiness metrics and avoid alerting or rolling back builds on the faulty premise that the user is experiencing unexpected sign-in prompts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-192">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-192">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-193">**FlowEndTime** – čas, ko se konča izpis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-193">**FlowEndTime** - the time when the sign out action ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-194">**FlowStartTime** – čas, ko se začne izpis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-194">**FlowStartTime** - the time when the sign out action started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-195">**IdentityErrorState** – stanje napake identitete pri izpisu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-195">**IdentityErrorState** - any identity error state during sign out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-196">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** – šifrirani ID identitete pri izpisu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-196">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** - the encrypted identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-197">**IdentityProviderType** – ponudnik identitete za identiteto, za katero poteka izpis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-197">**IdentityProviderType** - the identity provider of the identity being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-198">**IdentityUniqueID** – ID identitete, za katero poteka izpis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-198">**IdentityUniqueID** - the identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-199">**SessionEndTime** – čas, ko se konča seja dogodka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-199">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-200">**SignOutUserAction** – ponazarja, da je uporabnik začel postopek izpisa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-200">**SignOutUserAction** - Indicates the user initiates the sign out action</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysspipromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-201">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-201">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-202">Dogodki se zberejo, ko Office uporabniku prikaže poziv za vpis prek vmesnika SSPI v sistemu Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-202">Collected when Office shows the user a Windows SSPI sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-203">Poleg tihih pridobitev žetonov se s pozivi za preverjanje pristnosti ugotovi, ali je za uporabnika aktivirano stanje prekinjenega preverjanja pristnosti. Rezultat tega je stanje odjemalca brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-203">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-204">Prekinjeno preverjanje pristnosti lahko prepreči pridobitev licence in onemogoči odjemalca v celoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-204">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-205">Pozivi vmesnika SSPI v sistemu Windows se uporabljajo za preverjanje pristnosti z Exchangeom (za sinhronizacijo pošte), ko vir za Exchange uporabnika ni bil nastavljen za večkratno preverjanje pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-205">Windows SSPI prompts are used for authenticating with Exchange (for mail synchronizing) when the user's Exchange resource hasn't been setup for multi-factor authentication.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-206">Ti dogodki se skupaj z dogodki imenskega prostora Office.MATS uporabljajo za te namene:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-206">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-207">1\) Ugotovite, ali odjemalci lahko uspešno pridobijo žeton za preverjanje pristnosti oziroma je za njih aktivirano stanje prekinjenega preverjanja pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-207">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-208">2\) Ovrednotite, ali je prišlo do sprememb v odjemalcu, oziroma je v storitvah prišlo do kritičnih regresij glede izkušnje in zanesljivosti pri preverjanju pristnosti uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-208">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-209">3\) Ko se pojavijo napake, ti signali iz odgovorne komponente (koda odjemalca za Office, knjižnice za preverjanje pristnosti ali storitve avtoritete) oddajo pomembne kode napak, ki se jih lahko uporabi za triažo, diagnosticiranje ali odpravljanje napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-209">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-210">4\) Ti signali ponazarjajo različne pripravljenosti na odpremo in nadzirajo stanja, zaradi katerih se aktivirajo opozorila. Na ta način naši inženirji lahko hitro ukrepajo in skrajšajo čas za odpravljanje kritičnih težav blokiranja uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-210">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-211">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-211">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-212">**AllowSavedCreds** – ali se ohranijo nove poverilnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-212">**AllowSavedCreds** - whether the new credential is persisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-213">**AuthScheme** – uporabljena shema za preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-213">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-214">**CredsSaved** – ali se shranijo nove poverilnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-214">**CredsSaved** - whether the new credential is saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-215">**DocumentUrlHash** – zahteva za šifrirani URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-215">**DocumentUrlHash** - the encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-216">**EndTag** – oznaka, pri kateri se konča poziv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-216">**EndTag** - the tag where the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-217">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – ali je nova identiteta veljavna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-217">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – whether the new identity is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-218">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** – šifrirani ID nove identitete, ko je poziv končan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-218">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** - the encrypted new identity ID after prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-219">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – novi ponudnik identitete, ko je poziv končan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-219">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-220">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – ID nove identitete, ko je poziv končan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-220">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-221">**OutStatus** – ali je rezultat poziva veljaven</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-221">**OutStatus** - whether the prompt output is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-222">**PromptEndTime** – čas, ko se je poziv končal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-222">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-223">**PromptFailedTag** – oznaka, ki ponazarja napako vmesnika SSPI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-223">**PromptFailedTag** - the tag that indicates SSPI prompt failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-224">**PromptFlow** – oznaka, ki je priklicala poziv vmesnika SSPI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-224">**PromptFlow** - the tag that invoked the SSPI prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-225">**PromptStartTime** – čas, ko se je poziv začel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-225">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-226">**Proxy** – ali se uporablja strežnik proxy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-226">**Proxy** - if proxy is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-227">**ServerHash** – šifrirani naslov strežnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-227">**ServerHash** - the encrypted server address</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-228">**SessionEndTime** – čas, ko se konča seja dogodka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-228">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-229">**Timeout** – čas, ko je potekla časovna omejitev poziva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-229">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-230">**UiMessage** – sporočilo uporabniškega vmesnika v pozivu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-230">**UiMessage** - the UI message in the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-231">**UserNameHash** – šifrirano uporabniško ime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-231">**UserNameHash** - the encrypted user name</span></span>

### <a name="officematsactionofficewin32-officematsactionofficewinrt"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-261">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-261">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-262">Ta opis velja za dogodke Win32 in WinRT (ime je odvisno od platforme).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-262">The following description applies for both Win32 and WinRT events (the name depends on platform.)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-263">Microsoftov telemetrični sistem za preverjanje pristnosti (MATS) se zbere, ko Office poskuša pridobiti žeton za preverjanje pristnosti (na tih način ali prek poziva).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-263">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-264">Če pridobitev ni uspešna, so vključeni tudi podatki o napakah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-264">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-265">S temi dogodki se naši uporabniki lahko izognejo stanju prekinjenega preverjanja pristnosti tako, da:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-265">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-266">1\) Ugotovijo, ali odjemalci lahko uspešno pridobijo žeton za preverjanje pristnosti oziroma je za njih aktivirano stanje prekinjenega preverjanja pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-266">1\) Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-267">2\) Ovrednotijo, kdaj je prišlo do sprememb v odjemalcu ali storitvah, ali je prišlo do kritičnih regresij glede izkušnje in zanesljivosti pri preverjanju pristnosti uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-267">2\) Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-268">3\) Ko se pojavijo napake, ti signali iz odgovorne komponente (koda odjemalca za Office, knjižnice za preverjanje pristnosti ali storitve avtoritete) oddajo pomembne kode napak, ki se jih lahko uporabi za triažo, diagnosticiranje ali odpravljanje napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-268">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-269">4\) Ti signali ponazarjajo različne pripravljenosti na odpremo in nadzirajo stanja, zaradi katerih se aktivirajo opozorila. Na ta način naši inženirji lahko hitro ukrepajo in skrajšajo čas za odpravljanje kritičnih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-269">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-270">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-270">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-271">**Actiontype** – katera vrsta knjižnice za preverjanje pristnosti se uporabi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-271">**Actiontype** - Which authentication library is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-272">**Appaudience** – ali je aplikacija namenjena za notranjo oziroma zunanjo uporabo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-272">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-273">**Appforcedprompt** – ali aplikacija preglasi predpomnilnik in vsili prikaz poziva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-273">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-274">**Appname** – ima aplikacije, ki izvaja preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-274">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-275">**Appver** – različica aplikacije, ki izvaja preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-275">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-276">**Askedforcreds** – ali ja aplikacija uporabnika pozvala za vnos poverilnic za to dejanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-276">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-277">**Authoutcome** – ali je bil poskus preverjanja pristnosti uspešen, ni bil uspešen oziroma je bil preklican</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-277">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-278">**Blockingprompt** – ali je aplikacija prikazala poziv, ki zahteva posredovanje uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-278">**Blockingprompt** - Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-279">**Correlationid** – GUID, ki se uporablja za združevanje s podatki storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-279">**Correlationid** - GUID used for joining with services data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-280">**Count** – število dogodkov v primerih združevanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-280">**Count** - Count of events in cases of aggregation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-281">**Data\_accounttype** – potrošniški račun ali račun organizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-281">**Data\_accounttype** - Consumer or organizational account</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-282">**Devicenetworkstate** – ali je bil uporabnik dosegljiv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-282">**Devicenetworkstate** - Was the user online</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-283">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** – anonimni ID naprave, ki se uporablja za merjenje izkušnje naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-283">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-284">**Duration** – čas trajanja preverjanja pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-284">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-285">**Endtime** – ali se je dogodek preverjanja pristnosti končal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-285">**Endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-286">**Error** – koda napake, če preverjanje pristnosti ni bilo uspešno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-286">**Error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-287">**ErrorDescription** – kratek opis napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-287">**Errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-288">**Errorsource** – ali je do napake prišlo v storitvi, knjižnici za preverjanje pristnosti oziroma aplikaciji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-288">**Errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-289">**Identityservice** – ali je bil priklican Microsoftov račun storitve (MSA) oziroma storitev Azure Active Directory (AAD) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-289">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-290">**Interactiveauthcontainer** – katere vrste poziv je bil prikazan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-290">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-291">**Issilent** – ali je bil prikazan poziv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-291">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-292">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** – različica knjižnice Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-292">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** - Version of the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** – koda napake, ki jo je ustvarila knjižnica za preverjanje pristnosti za ta poskus preverjanja pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** - Error code emitted by authentication library for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** – API, ki je bil priklican za ta poskus preverjanja pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** - API invoked for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – URL overovitelja za Azure Active Directory, ki je odgovoren za preverjanje pristnosti uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – Azure Active Directory authority URL responsible for authenticating the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – potrošnik/pogodba za storitve Microsoft (MSA) v primerjavi z organizacijskim/Azure Active Directory (AAD); trenutno vedno AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – Consumer / Microsoft Service Agreement (MSA) vs organizational / Azure Active Directory (AAD); currently always AAD</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – ponazarja, ali je bilo preverjanje pristnosti v storitvi dokončano</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – Tells whether authentication completed on the service-side</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** – ponazarja, ali je ADAL pri preverjanju pristnosti uporabil posrednika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** - Tells whether ADAL used a broker for authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-299">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – ponazarja ime posrednika (npr. upravljanje računov v sistemu Windows)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-299">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – Tells the name of the broker (e.g., Windows Account Management)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** – ponazarja različico morebitnega posrednika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** - Tells the version of the broker if used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-301">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** – število dogodkov predpomnilnik, ki jih je ADAL izvedel med pridobivanjem žetona</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-301">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** - Number of cache events ADAL performed while retrieving token</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-302">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** – če se združi ta signal, ponazarja največje dovoljeno število dogodkov predpomnilnika za katere koli združene dogodke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-302">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-303">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** – če se združi ta signal, ponazarja najmanjše dovoljeno število dogodkov predpomnilnika za katere koli združene dogodke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-303">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-304">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** – če se združi ta signal, ponazarja vsoto dogodkov predpomnilnika za vse združene dogodke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-304">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the cache events of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-305">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** – kolikokrat je API prebral iz predpomnilnika diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-305">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** - How many times the API read from the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-306">Na voljo, če je bilo zaznano vsaj eno branje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-306">Present if there was at least one read.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-307">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** – kolikokrat ni uspelo branje iz predpomnilnika diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-307">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache read failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-308">Na voljo, če je bil zaznan vsaj en neuspešen poskus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-308">Is present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-309">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** – koda napake ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-309">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-310">Na voljo, če je bilo zaznano vsaj eno neuspešno branje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-310">Present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-311">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** – koda napake sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-311">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-312">Na voljo, če je bilo zaznano vsaj eno neuspešno branje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-312">Is present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-313">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** – kolikokrat je API zapisal v predpomnilnik diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-313">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** - How many times the API wrote to the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-314">Na voljo, če je bilo zaznano vsaj eno pisanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-314">Present if there was at least one write.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** – kolikokrat ni uspelo pisanje v predpomnilnik diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache-write failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-316">Na voljo, če je bil zaznan vsaj en neuspešen poskus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-316">Present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** – koda napake ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-318">Na voljo, če je bila zaznana vsaj ena napaka pisanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-318">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-319">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** – koda napake sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-319">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-320">Na voljo, če je bila zaznana vsaj ena napaka pisanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-320">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** – zgoščeni ID aplikacije AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** - Hashed AAD app ID</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** – trditev true/false, ki ponazarja, ali je žeton presegel svojo življenjsko dobo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** - True/false telling if the token has an extended lifetime.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-323">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun**t – število klicev HTTP, ki jih izvede ADAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-323">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun**t - Count of HTTP calls made by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** – če je združen ta signal, ponazarja največje dovoljeno število klicev HTTP, ki jih izvede ADAL za kateri koli združeni dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** – če je združen ta signal, ponazarja najmanjše dovoljeno število klicev HTTP, ki jih izvede ADAL za kateri koli združeni dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-326">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** – če je združen ta signal, ponazarja vsoto klicev HTTP, ki jih izvede ADAL za vse združene dogodke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-326">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the HTTP calls made by ADAL of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-327">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_silent\_ui** – trditev true/false, ki ponazarja, ali je ADAL prikazal poziv uporabniškega vmesnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-327">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_silent\_ui** - True/false telling if UI was shown (prompt) by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-328">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_successful** – trditev true/false, ki ponazarja, ali je bil API ADAL uspešen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-328">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_successful** - True/false telling if ADAL API succeeded.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-329">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** – trditev true/false, ki ponazarja, ali je omogočen celoten način pisanja dnevnika ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-329">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** - True/false telling if ADAL full logging mode is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-330">Ti podatke so zapisani v dnevnik samo lokalno in niso posredovani telemetriji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-330">This data is only logged locally, not emitted in telemetry.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-331">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_oauth\_error\_code** – koda napake za protokol OAuth, ki jo vrne storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-331">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_oauth\_error\_code** – OAuth protocol error code returned by the service.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-332">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_prompt\_behavior** – parameter HTTP za prijavo, ki je bil posredovan storitvi za določanje, ali je mogoče prikazati uporabniški vmesnik (oziroma storitvi ni bil posredovan noben parameter HTTP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-332">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_prompt\_behavior** - log-in or none HTTP parameter passed to service to specify if user interface can be shown.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-352">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_user\_cancel** – trditev true/false, ali je bilo preklicano okno uporabniškega vmesnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-352">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_user\_cancel** - True / false if the user interface window was canceled.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotesigninssoexternalappsaccountfound"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-366">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-366">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-367">Ta dogodek se zabeleži, ko je račun z veljavnim žetonom za osveževanje najden med seznamom računov, ki jih je predložil TokenSharingManager.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-367">This event is logged when an account with a valid refresh token is found among the list of accounts provided by TokenSharingManager.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-368">Ta primer je specifičen za enotno prijavo (SSO).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-368">This scenario is specific to Single Sign-on (SSO).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-370">**AccountType** – prijavi vrsto računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-370">**AccountType** - Logs the type of account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-371">**ProviderPackageID** – prijavi ID paketa za program, ki je priskrbel ta račun</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-371">**ProviderPackageID** - Logs the package ID of the app that provided this account</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-373">Ta dogodek se zabeleži, ko je prišlo do napake pri poskusu pridobivanja žetona za osveževanje za račun na seznamu računov, ki ga je predložil TokenSharingManager.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-373">This event is logged when there was an error when attempting to obtain a refresh token for an account in the list of accounts provided by TokenSharingManager.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-374">Ta primer je specifičen za enotno prijavo (SSO).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-374">This scenario is specific to Single Sign-on (SSO)</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-375">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-375">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunbootstrapper"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-384">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-384">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-385">Podatki o zalogi in nastavitvi Officea se zberejo, ko uporabnik zažene datoteko Office setup.exe, da spremeni nameščene Officeove izdelke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-385">Office set up and inventory data collected when the user is running Office setup.exe to modify their installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-386">Dogodki se uporabljajo za merjenje uspešnosti/neuspešnosti celotne namestitve Officea, ki jo je sprožil uporabnik, vključno z vnaprej zahtevanimi pregledi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-386">Used to measure success / failure of a full user-initiated Office installation including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-387">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-387">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-388">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – koda napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-388">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-389">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – funkcija, ki je ni bilo mogoče zagnati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-389">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-390">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – del, ki ga ni bilo mogoče izvesti v orodju boostrapperbootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-390">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – The part that we failed in the boostrapperbootstrapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-391">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – vrsta izjeme, ki je ni bilo mogoče izvesti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-391">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-392">**Data\_Culture** – lokalne nastavitve, uporabljene za zagon datoteke exe, npr. en-us</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-392">**Data\_Culture** - the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-393">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** – zgoščena vrednost sha-256 za žeton, prejeta od storitve OLS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-393">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** - a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-394">**Data\_Platform** – namestitev x64 ali x86</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-394">**Data\_Platform** - x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-395">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – zahtevana okvara, na katero smo naleteli, npr. operacijski sistem ni podprt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-395">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – The prerequisite failure we hit, i.e. the operating system is not supported</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-396">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** – izdelek, ki ga nameščamo, npr. Aplikacije ogrodja Microsoft 365 za podjetja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-396">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** - Product we're installing, i.e. Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruncorruptioncheck"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-397">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-397">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-398">Podatki o zalogi in nastavitvi Officea se zberejo, ko odjemalec zagona s klikom zažene poškodovano preverjanje, s katerim zagotovi, da so Officeove dvojiške vrednosti pravilne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-398">Office set up and inventory data collected when Click-to-Run client is running a corruption check to make sure that Office binaries are correct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-399">Dogodki se uporabljajo za merjenje poškodb Officeovih dvojiških vrednosti in določanje, katere dvojiške vrednosti so poškodovane.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-399">Used to measure corruption of Office binaries, and which binaries are corrupt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-400">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-400">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-401">**Data\_Active –** trenutni manifest toka, ki ga preverjamo na disku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-401">**Data\_Active -** The current stream manifest we're checking on disk</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-402">**Podatki\_ActivePackages –** katere pakete vsebuje manifest</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-402">**Data\_ActivePackages -** what packages the manifest contains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-403">**Data\_ActiveVersion –** različica manifesta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-403">**Data\_ActiveVersion -** the version of the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-404">**Data\_AddFileCount –** števil datotek, ki jih bomo dodali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-404">**Data\_AddFileCount -** how many files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-405">**Data\_AddFileFiles –** vzorec datotek, ki jih bomo dodali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-405">**Data\_AddFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-406">**Data\_CompressionLevel –** način stiskanja datotek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-406">**Data\_CompressionLevel -** how the files are compressed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-407">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel –** kako globoko preverjamo poškodbe (stopnje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-407">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel -** how deeply we're checking for corruption, stages</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-408">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount –** koliko datotek ima nepravilno velikost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-408">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount -** how many files have a corrupt size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-409">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles –** vzorec datotek z nepravilno velikostjo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-409">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-410">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount –** število datotek z nepravilno različico</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-410">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount -** how many files have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-411">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles –** vzorec datotek z nepravilnimi različicami</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-411">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-412">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount –** število datotek, ki jih ni bilo mogoče odpreti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-412">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount -** how many files we failed to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-413">**Data\_FileBadDigestFiles –** vzorec datotek, ki jih ni bilo mogoče odpreti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-413">**Data\_FileBadDigestFiles -** a sample of the files that we were unable to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-414">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount –** število nepodpisanih datotek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-414">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount -** have many files that aren't signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-415">**Data\_FileNotSignedFiles –** vzorec nepodpisanih datotek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-415">**Data\_FileNotSignedFiles -** a sample of the files that aren't signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-416">**Data\_FileNotTrustedCount –** število datotek, ki jim ni mogoče zaupati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-416">**Data\_FileNotTrustedCount -** how many files aren't trusted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-417">**Data\_FileNotTrustedFiles –** vzorec datotek, ki jim ni mogoče zaupati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-417">**Data\_FileNotTrustedFiles -** a sample of the files that we don't trust</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunmachinemetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-440">Office.ClickToRun.MachineMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-440">Office.ClickToRun.MachineMetadata</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-441">Podatki o zalogi in nastavitvi Officea, ki omogočajo zahtevane metapodatke za nastavitev in zalogo ter se uporabljajo za določanje natančne zbirke namestitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-441">Office set up and inventory data that provides necessary metadata for setup and inventory and is used to determine an accurate install base.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-443">**Data\_C2RClientVer** – različica datoteke OfficeClickToRun.exe v računalniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-443">**Data\_C2RClientVer** – The version of OfficeClickToRun.exe on the machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-444">**Data\_OfficeBitness** – bitni način, v katerem je nameščen Office, x86 ali x64</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-444">**Data\_OfficeBitness** – The bitness that Office is installed in, x86 or x64</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-445">**Data\_OfficeVersion** – različica nameščenega Officea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-445">**Data\_OfficeVersion** - The version Office is installed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-446">**Data\_Sku** – inventarna enota, ki je nameščena, tj. Aplikacije ogrodja Microsoft 365 za podjetja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-446">**Data\_Sku** - The SKU that's installed, i.e. Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-447">**Data\_SqmMachineID** – enolični ID računalnika, ki ga uporablja Windows SQM Data\_SusClientID – identifikator za posodobitev Officea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-447">**Data\_SqmMachineID** – Unique Machine ID used by Windows SQM Data\_SusClientID- Machine Office update identifier</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunodt"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-448">Office.ClickToRun.ODT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-448">Office.ClickToRun.ODT</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-449">Podatki o zalogi in nastavitvi Officea, ki se zberejo, ko skrbnik za IT zažene datoteko setup.exe s tehnologijo zagona s klikom za orodje za uvedbo sistema Office, da spremeni Officeove izdelke, ki jih je namestil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-449">Office set up and inventory data collected when an IT Admin is running the Office Deployment Tool Click-to-Run setup.exe to modify their users' installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-450">Dogodki se uporabljajo za merjenje uspešnosti/neuspešnosti celotne namestitve Officea, ki jo je sprožil skrbnik za IT, vključno z vnaprej zahtevanimi pregledi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-450">It is used to measure success / failure of full IT Admin initiated Office installations including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-451">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-451">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-452">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – koda napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-452">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode-** The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-453">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – funkcija, ki je ni bilo mogoče zagnati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-453">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource-** The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-454">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – del, ki ga ni bilo mogoče izvesti v orodju boostrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-454">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState-** The part that we failed in the boot-strapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-455">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – vrsta izjeme, ki je ni bilo mogoče izvesti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-455">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType-** The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-456">**Data\_ConfigurationHost** – gostitelj, ki je posredoval datoteko configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-456">**Data\_ConfigurationHost-** The host where the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-457">**Data\_ConfigurationId** – ID, ki ga pridobimo iz datoteke configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-457">**Data\_ConfigurationId-** The ID we get from a configuration.xml</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-458">**Data\_ConfigurationSource** – vir, ki je posredoval datoteko configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-458">**Data\_ConfigurationSource-** We the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-459">**Data\_Culture** – lokalne nastavitve, uporabljene za zagon datoteke exe, npr. en-us</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-459">**Data\_Culture-** the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-460">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** – zgoščena vrednost sha-256 za žeton, prejeta od storitve OLS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-460">**Data\_HashedOLSToken-** a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-461">**Data\_MigrateArchRequest** – če uporabnika selimo iz načina x86 v x64 ali obratno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-461">**Data\_MigrateArchRequest-** If we are migrating the user from x86 to x64 or vice-versa</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-462">**Data\_MigrateArchRequestValid** – če menimo, da je zahteva za selitev veljavna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-462">**Data\_MigrateArchRequestValid-** If we believe the migrate request is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-463">**Data\_Platform** – namestitev x64 ali x86</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-463">**Data\_Platform-** x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-464">**Data\_PlatformMigratedFrom** – začetna platforma, npr. x86</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-464">**Data\_PlatformMigratedFrom-** Starting platform, i.e. x86</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-465">**Data\_PlatformMigratedTo** – končna platforma, npr x64</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-465">**Data\_PlatformMigratedTo-** Ending platform, i.e. x64</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-466">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – zahtevana okvara, do katere je prišlo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-466">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type-** The prerequisite failure we hit</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-467">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** – izdelek, ki ga nameščamo, npr. Aplikacije ogrodja Microsoft 365 za podjetja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-467">**Data\_ProductReleaseId-** Product we're installing, i.e. Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunrepomanlogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-468">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-468">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-469">Poroča o stanju novega posodobitvenega cevovoda »Zagon s klikom« (»Repoman«), če pa se uspešno prenese, uveljavi posodobitve za Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-469">Reports on the status for the new Click-to-Run update pipeline ("Repoman") and if it successfully downloads and applies Office updates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-470">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-470">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-471">**ApplySucceeded** – ima vrednost true, če je cevovod uspešno uveljavil posodobitev, v nasprotnem primeru pa vrednost false.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-471">**ApplySucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully applied an Office update, false if not.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-472">**DownloadSucceeded** – ima vrednost true, če je cevovod uspešno prenesel posodobitev, v nasprotnem primeru pa vrednost false.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-472">**DownloadSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully downloaded an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-473">**ErrorCode** – koda zadnje napake, ki se je pojavila v cevovodu »Zagon s klikom« Repoman.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-473">**ErrorCode -** The code of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-474">**ErrorCode** – dodatne podrobnosti zadnje napake, ki se je pojavila v cevovodu »Zagon s klikom« Repoman.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-474">**ErrorDetails -**  Additional error details of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-475">**ErrorMessage** – sporočilo zadnje napake, ki se je pojavila v cevovodu »Zagon s klikom« Repoman.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-475">**ErrorMessage -** The message of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-476">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded** – ima vrednost true, če cevovod uspešno ustvari sejo za pretakanje Officeove posodobitve, v nasprotnem primeru pa vrednost false.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-476">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully creates a session for streaming an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-477">**RepomanErrorMessage** – iz datoteke repoman.dll je bilo prejeto sporočilo o napaki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-477">**RepomanErrorMessage -** The error message received from the repoman.dll.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-486">**Data\_16\_SourceType** – mesto vira za Office 16, npr. CDN ali lokalno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-486">**Data\_16\_SourceType -** Where the Office 16 source is located i.e. CDN or Local</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-487">**Data\_16\_UpdatesEnabled** – ali so omogočene posodobitve za Office 16</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-487">**Data\_16\_UpdatesEnabled -** If Office 16 updates are enabled</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-488">**Data\_16\_UpdateVersion** – različica, na katero bo posodobljen Office 16</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-488">**Data\_16\_UpdateVersion -** What version of Office 16 we're updating to</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-489">**Data\_16\_Version** – različica za Office 16</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-489">**Data\_16\_Version -** The Office 16 version</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-490">**Data\_AddingFixedProducts** – izdelki, ki jih bomo dodali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-490">**Data\_AddingFixedProducts -** The products we're adding</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-491">**Data\_AddingProducts** – katere izdelke naj dodamo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-491">**Data\_AddingProducts -** What products we're asked to add</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-492">**Data\_CompletionState** – ali smo dokončali opravilo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-492">**Data\_CompletionState -** If we completed the task</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-493">**Data\_ErrorCode** – koda napake, zaradi katere ni bilo mogoče dokončati opravila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-493">**Data\_ErrorCode -** The error code we failed with</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-494">**Data\_ErrorDetails** – dodatne podrobnosti napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-494">**Data\_ErrorDetails -** Extra details about an error</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-495">**Data\_ErrorMessage** – sporočilo napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-495">**Data\_ErrorMessage -** An error message on what went wrong</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-496">**Data\_ErrorSource** – mesto napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-496">**Data\_ErrorSource -** Where the error took place</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-499">**Data\_IsErrorCodeIgnorableForScenarioHealth** – ali menimo, da je kodo napake mogoče prezreti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-499">**Data\_IsErrorCodeIgnorableForScenarioHealth -** If we believe the error code is ignorable</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruntransportexperimentaltransportpipelinecreatetransport"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1433">Office.ClickToRun.Transport.ExperimentalTransport.PipelineCreateTransport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1433">Office.ClickToRun.Transport.ExperimentalTransport.PipelineCreateTransport</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1434">Podatki o zalogi in nastavitvi Officea se zberejo, ko odjemalec s tehnologijo zagona s klikom ustvarja tok za prenos Officeovih datotek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1434">Office set up and inventory data collected when the Click-to-Run client is creating a transport stream to download Office files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1435">Dogodki se uporabljajo za določanja stanja različnih tehnologij prenosa (npr. HTTP, BITS, SO), kar je kritičnega pomena za pravilno prenašanje Officea za namestitev in posodobitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1435">Used for determining the health of various transport technologies (e.g., HTTP, BITS, DO) which is critical to downloading Office properly for installation and updates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1436">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1436">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1437">**Data\_IsForeGroundStreaming** – ali pretočno predvajamo v ospredje oziroma ozadje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1437">**Data\_IsForeGroundStreaming** – If we're streaming in the foreground or background</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1438">**Data\_IsInstallMode** – ima vrednost 1, če nameščamo in prenašamo datoteke, oziroma vrednost 0, če jih ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1438">**Data\_IsInstallMode** – 1 if we're installing and downloading files, 0 if not</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1439">**Data\_SourceProtocol** – ali prenašamo iz podatkovnega omrežja vsebine, CDN-ja, računalnika, ki predstavlja mesto namestitve, lokalno ali iz vira v lokalnem območnem omrežju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1439">**Data\_SourceProtocol –** If we're downloading from a content data network, CDN, the machine we're installing on, local, or from a resource on the local area network,</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1440">**Data\_Status** – uspeh ali neuspeh</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1440">**Data\_Status** – Success or failure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1442">Podatki o zalogi in nastavitvi Officea se zberejo, ko odjemalec s tehnologijo zagona s klikom končuje stanje posodobitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1442">Office set up and inventory data collected when the Click-to-Run client is finishing an update status</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorununiversalbootstrapperapplication"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1450">Office.ClickToRun.UniversalBootstrapper.Application</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1450">Office.ClickToRun.UniversalBootstrapper.Application</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1451">Poroča o rezultatu poskusa pokončne namestitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1451">Reports the result of the end-to-end installation attempt</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1452">**ErrorCode –** celoštevilska vrednost, povezana z neobravnavano izjemo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1452">**ErrorCode –**    Integer value associated with an unhandled exception</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1453">**ErrorDetails –** niz, v katerem je opisana lokacija, kjer je prišlo do neobravnavane izjeme (funkcija, datoteka, številka vrstice, dodatni parametri, ki jih je nastavil gumb »thrower«)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1453">**ErrorDetails –**    String that describes the location of where an unhandled exception occurred (function, file, line number, additional parameters set by the thrower)</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1455">**ErrorType –** niz z opisom kategorije neobravnavane izjeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1455">**ErrorType –**    String describing the category of an unhandled exception</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1456">**ExitCode –** celo število, ki je povezano z rezultatom zagona Bootstrapper, pri čemer je razvidno, da je uspeh v primerjavi s posebnimi vrstami spodletelih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1456">**ExitCode –**    Integer value associated with the result of running the bootstrapper, indicating success vs. specific types of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1532">**SharedComputerLicensing –** logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je skrbnik za IT zahteval nastavitev, ki omogoča funkcijo »SharedComputerLicensing«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1532">**SharedComputerLicensing –**    Boolean indicating whether an IT Admin requested setup to enable the "SharedComputerLicensing" feature</span></span>

XML</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1533">**ShouldActivate–**    Boolean indicating whether an IT Admin requested an automatic licensing activation attempt in their configuration.xml</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1541">**CMDMode –** prijazen niz, ki ustreza celotnemu načinu zamenjave načina je bil zaznan v argumentih cmd, ki so bili preneseni v exe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1541">**CMDMode –**    The friendly string corresponding to which overall mode switch was detected in the cmd arguments passed to the exe.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1542">Možnosti so: Autorun, Configure, Consumer, download, Help, pakirnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1542">Possibilities are:  autorun, configure, consumer, download, help, packager</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1543">**DeliveryMechanism –** GUID »FFNRoot«, ki je bil pridobljen iz XML deskriptorja različic (ki ga je ožigosal RDX), v katerem je navedeno, za katero publiko/kanal je prišel vir gradnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1543">**DeliveryMechanism –**    The "FFNRoot" guid extracted from the Version Descriptor XML (stamped by RDX), which tells us which audience/channel the build source came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1546">**ErrorDetails –** niz, v katerem je opisana lokacija, kjer je prišlo do neobravnavane izjeme (funkcija, datoteka, številka vrstice, dodatni parametri, ki jih je nastavil gumb »thrower«)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1546">**ErrorDetails –**    String that describes the location of where an unhandled exception occurred (function, file, line number, additional parameters set by the thrower)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1547">**ErrorMessage –** niz, ki je definiran na mestu, kjer je bila zavrnjena neobravnavana izjema, z opisom narave napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1547">**ErrorMessage –**    String defined at the point where an unhandled exception was thrown, describing the nature of the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1548">**ErrorType –** niz z opisom kategorije neobravnavane izjeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1548">**ErrorType –**    String describing the category of an unhandled exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1549">**ExitCode –** celo število, ki je povezano z rezultatom zagona izvršitvene faze Bootstrapper, pri čemer je navedeno, da je uspeh v primerjavi s posebnimi vrstami spodletelih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1549">**ExitCode –**    Integer value associated with the result of running the Execute phase of the bootstrapper, indicating success vs. specific types of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1552">**PreReqResult –** celo število enum vrednosti rezultata, ko so bile izvedene predzahtevi kontrole (pass/neuspel/ponovni zagon)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1552">**PreReqResult –**    The integer enum value of the result when PreReq checks were performed (pass/fail/re-run)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1553">**UnexpectedAction –** »TRUE«, če je v tej namestitvi načrtovano opravilo »UnexpectedAction« (primer napake)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1553">**UnexpectedAction –**    "true" if the UnexpectedAction task (an error case) is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>
