### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1555">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1555">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1556">*[Ta dogodek je bil odstranjen iz trenutnih graditev Officea, vendar se bo morda še vedo pojavljal v starejših graditvah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1556">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1557">Ta dogodek uporabljamo za pridobivanje standardnih metapodatkov pri vsakem zagonu dodatka zaloge, ki je del upravitelja dosegljivosti storitve za Office, in se uporablja za Officeove informacije o zalogi v teh računalnikih, ki jih je izbral skrbnik za IT.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1557">This event is used to acquire standard metadata on each run of the Inventory add-on, which is part of the Office Serviceability Manager and is used for inventory Office information on those machines for which an IT admin has opted in.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1558">Metapodatki, ki so tukaj zanimivi, je ID seje, ki se uporablja za povezovanje z drugimi podatki, shranjenimi v najemniški storitvi v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1558">The metadata of specific interest here is the session ID, and it is used for linking to other data stored within a per-tenant cloud service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1559">Ta dogodek ne vsebuje dodatnih polj, kajti pomembni so zgolj metapodatki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1559">This event contains no extra fields since only the metadata is relevant.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1560">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1560">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1561">Ta dogodek se zabeleži, ko se pokličete v WebService, ki je bil ustvarjen z dodatkom upravitelja za uporabnost s tehnologijo »zagon s klikom«, ne glede na to, ali je uspešen ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1561">This event is logged when the call to the webservice made within the Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager Inventory add-on completes, irrespective of whether it succeeds or fails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1562">To je pravzaprav zadnji postopek v Dodatku za spremljanje stanja celotnega postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1562">This is essentially the last operation within the add-on to track the overall operation status.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1563">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1563">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1564">**ActionDetail** – dodatne podrobnosti o tem, kdaj pride do napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1564">**ActionDetail** -  Additional details for when a failure occurs.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1565">Če je zahteve HTTP uspešna, bo ActionDetail 0.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1565">If the HTTP request succeeds, ActionDetail will be 0.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1566">Če polje z rezultati ni v redu (tj. ne 0), kar pomeni, da zahteva ni poslana, bo v tem polju zapisana Notranja koda napake, ki je enaka kot polje z rezultatom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1566">If the Result field is not OK (i.e. not 0), which means that the request is not sent, this field will log the internal error code which is the same as the Result field.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1567">Če je polje rezultat v redu (tj. 0), kar pomeni, da je koda odziva HTTP > = 300, se bo prijavila koda za odziv HTTP (na primer 404).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1567">If the Result field is OK (i.e. 0), which means that the HTTP response code >= 300, it will log the HTTP response code (e.g. 404).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1568">**Rezultat** – številske zastavice kode napake, ki jih vrne Office WebService Call API-ji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1568">**Result** - Numeric error code flags returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1569">– na primer 3 pomeni, da je prišlo do težave z inicializacijo glav HTTP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1569">– e.g. 3 would mean that there was a problem initializing the HTTP headers.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1570">**Vnesite** – dodatne informacije vrste.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1570">**Type** - Additional type information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1571">V primeru inventarja te informacije določa vrsto poslanega tovora – na primer polno ali samo Delta sprememb.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1571">In the case of the Inventory, this information specifies the type of payload being sent – e.g. full or just a delta of changes.</span></span> 

-  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1572">**WebCallSource** – vrednost enumeracije (ki je navedena kot celo število), ki označuje dodatek upravitelja za uporabnost, ki je bil vir klica:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1572">**WebCallSource** - An enumeration value (specified as an integer) indicating the Serviceability Manager add-on that was the source of the call:</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1573">Zaloga: 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1573">Inventory: 0</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1574">Konfiguracija inventarja: 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1574">Inventory Configuration: 1</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1575">Pravilnik o inventarju: 2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1575">Inventory Policy: 2</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1576">Stanje omrežnega inventarja: 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1576">Inventory Network Status: 3</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1577">Upravitelj uporabnosti: 4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1577">Serviceability Manager: 4</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1578">Upravljanje: 5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1578">Manageability: 5</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerwebservicefailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1579">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1579">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1580">Kadar koli klic spletne storitve v okviru dodatkov Office Serviceability Manager ne uspe, je ta izjava zabeležena v dnevnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1580">Whenever a call to a webservice within one of the Office Serviceability Manager add-ins fails, this statement is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1581">Do napak lahko pride zaradi notranjih napak ali nezmožnosti vzpostavitve povezave s spletno storitvijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1581">Failures can be due to internal failures or an inability to connect to the webservice.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1582">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1582">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1583">**Dodatek** – dodatek upravitelja s tehnologijo »zagon s klikom«, iz katerega je bil ustvarjen klic za WebService.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1583">**Add-on** - The Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager add-on from which the webservice call was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1584">To lahko vsebuje vrednosti, kot so inventar, obvladljivost itd. kodirano kot številska vrednost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1584">This can have values like inventory, manageability, etc. encoded as a numeric value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1585">**ID korelacije** – naključno ustvarjen GUID, ki je specifičen za trenutni primerek, ki je poslan v WebService za korelacijo klicev med odjemalcem in strežnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1585">**Correlation ID** - A randomly generated GUID specific to the current instance that is sent to the webservice to correlate calls between the client and the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1586">**ErrorInfo** – števila podatkov kode napake, ki jih vrne Office WebService Call API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1586">**ErrorInfo** - Numeric error code information returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1587">**ErrorMessage** – sporočilo, ki nudi dodatne vpoglede v napako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1587">**ErrorMessage** - A message providing further insight into the failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1588">Vsaka vrsta napake je preslikana v kodiran niz, nekatere vrste napak pa so lahko preslikane v več nizov, odvisno od vrste napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1588">Each error type maps to a hardcoded string, with some error types mapping to potentially multiple strings depending on the specific nature of the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1589">**Funkcija** – funkcija v kodi, iz katere je prišlo do trenutnega klica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1589">**Function** - The function in the code from which the current call occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1590">**Stanje** – koda stanja HTTP, ki jo vrne klic v WebService, na primer 404, 500 itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1590">**Status** - The HTTP status code returned by the call to the webservice, e.g. 404, 500, etc.</span></span>


## <a name="enhanced-configuration-service-ecs-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1591">Dogodki izboljšane konfiguracijske storitve (ECS)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1591">Enhanced Configuration Service (ECS) events</span></span>

### <a name="officeexperimentationfeaturequerybatched"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1592">Office.Experimentation.FeatureQueryBatched</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1592">Office.Experimentation.FeatureQueryBatched</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1593">Zbere informacije o vratih funkcije/vratih spremembe, ki jih poizvede izvedena koda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1593">Collects information about Feature gates/Change gates queried by executed code.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1594">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1594">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1595">**Count** – število poizvedenih vrat funkcije v tem paketnem dogodku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1595">**Count** - Number of queried feature gates in this batched event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1596">**Features** – informacije o poizvedenih vratih</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1596">**Features** - Information about the queried gate.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1597">**Sequence** – vrstni red, v katerem so bila poizvedena vrata FeatureGate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1597">**Sequence** - Order in which FeatureGate was queried</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingaccepteulaforcurrentlicense"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1616">Office.Licensing.AcceptEulaForCurrentLicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1616">Office.Licensing.AcceptEulaForCurrentLicense</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1617">Ti dogodki so zbrani, ko uporabnik prejme licenco in sprejme licenčne pogoje za Microsoftovo programsko opremo za trenutno licenco.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1617">This is collected when the user gets licensed and accepts EULA for the current license</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1618">Dogodki se uporabljajo za zaznavanje, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju, za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1618">It is used to detect if the user is in a good state or not, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1619">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1619">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1620">**ACID** – identifikator GUID, ki predstavlja Officeov izdelek, za katerega je uporabnik prejel licenco</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1620">**ACID** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1621">**DwEulaId** – številski identifikator za vrsto licenčnih pogojev za Microsoftovo programsko opremo, ki jo je sprejel uporabnik</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1621">**DwEulaId** – Numeric identifier of the type of EULA that was just accepted by the user</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingactivation"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1622">Office.Licensing.Activation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1622">Office.Licensing.Activation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1623">Naknadna nastavitev licence v stroju, kjer licenco poskušamo aktivirati s klicem storitve AVS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1623">Post setting up the license on the machine, we attempt to activate the license by calling the AVS service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1624">Sporoča rezultat aktivacijskega klica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1624">This reports the result of the activation call</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1625">Dogodki so pomembni pri zaznavanju, koliko uporabnikov ima težave pri aktivaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1625">It is critical in detecting how many users are facing activation issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1626">Poskrbeli smo za zaznavanje anomalije, s katero zaznamo morebitno regresijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1626">We have anomaly detection to detect any regression.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1627">To je izjemno pomembno, saj imamo zunanje odvisnosti v storitvi AVS, ta signal pa ponazarja, ali naši zunanji partnerji delujejo ustrezno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1627">This is super critical as we have an external dependency on AVS and this signal points whether our external partners are healthy .</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1628">Te dogodke prav tako uporabljamo za diagnostične namene in preverjanje stanja sistema, ko uporabnik posreduje težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1628">It is also used for diagnostic purposes and system health if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1629">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1629">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1630">**Acid** – identifikator GUID, ki predstavlja Officeov izdelek, za katerega je uporabnik prejel licenco</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1630">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1631">**ReferralData** – identifikator za OEM, ki se namesti v Office v računalniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1631">**ReferralData** – Identifier of the OEM that installed Office on the machine</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingactivationwizard"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1632">Office.Licensing.ActivationWizard</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1632">Office.Licensing.ActivationWizard</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1633">Če iz neznanega razloga nismo uspeli samodejno aktivirati licence, uporabniku prikažemo čarovnika za aktivacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1633">If we are not able to automatically activate the license for some reason, we show an activation wizard to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1634">Ti dogodki nam posredujejo informacije, da je bil čarovnih prikazan uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1634">This reports that the wizard is being shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1635">Dogodki so pomembni pri zaznavanju, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju in ima omogočeno vso funkcionalnost, se uporabljajo za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1635">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1636">Ta dogodek ne zbere nobenega polja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1636">This event collects no fields.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingenforcesigninqualified"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1637">Office.Licensing.EnforceSignInQualified</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1637">Office.Licensing.EnforceSignInQualified</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1638">To je signal, ki nam pove, ali je bil poskus, ki smo ga izvedli za vsilitev vpisa uporabnika v sklopu licenciranja, uspešen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1638">This is the signal that tells us if the experiment that we are running to enforce user sign as part of licensing is successful.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1639">To je ključnega pomena pri zaznavanju uspeha ali neuspeha poskusa, ki uporabnike prisili, da se prijavijo, kar predstavlja obvezen korak pri sodobnem licenciranju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1639">This is critical in detecting the success or failure of the experiment that is forcing the users to login which is a required step for the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1640">Če se uporabniki ne uspejo vpisati, ne bodo mogli več uporabljati aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1640">Failure to sign in will result in the users not being able to use the app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1641">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1641">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1642">**Qualified** – prepozna, ali je uporabnik kvalificiran za vsiljeni vpis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1642">**Qualified** – Identifies whether the user qualified for the sign in enforcement</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingexpirationdialogshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1643">Office.Licensing.ExpirationDialogShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1643">Office.Licensing.ExpirationDialogShown</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1644">Ti podatki so zbrani, ko se pojavi pogovorno okno poteka, v katerem uporabnik izve, da je potekla njegova licenca. Dogodki so pomembni pri zaznavanju, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju in ima omogočeno vso funkcionalnost, se uporabljajo za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1644">This is collected when we show the expiration dialog to the user that says that their license has expired It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1645">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1645">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1646">**LicNotificationState** – orodje za oštevilčenje, s katerim ugotovimo, katera vrsta obvestila je bila prikazana uporabniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1646">**LicNotificationState** – An enumerator that tells us what kind of notification is being shown to the user</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingfullvalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1647">Office.Licensing.FullValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1647">Office.Licensing.FullValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1648">Ti podatki so zbrani pri vsaki seji, ki sporoča stanje licenciranja v računalniku in sporoča napake, ki se prikažejo uporabniku, zaradi katerih, ne morejo uporabljati aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1648">This is collected on every session that reports the licensing state of the machine and reports the errors that the user is seeing due to which they are not able to use the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1649">Ta dogodek ponazarja, ali je stanje računalnika uporabnika primerno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1649">This event indicates if the user's machine is healthy or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1650">Za ta dogodek smo vzpostavili zaznavanje anomalije, s katerim ugotovimo, ali regresija ali mehanizem aktivacije povzroča nepravilno delovanje uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1650">We have anomaly detection set up for this event to indicate if a regression or activation mechanism is causing bad user behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1651">Ta dogodek je pomemben tudi pri diagnosticiranju težav uporabnika in za nadziranje zdravja sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1651">This is also critical when diagnosing user issues and for monitoring system health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1652">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1652">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1653">**Acid** – identifikator GUID, ki predstavlja Officeov izdelek, za katerega je uporabnik prejel licenco</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1653">**Acid** – A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1654">**ActivationAttributes** – vrsta mehanizma aktivacije, ki ga uporablja uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1654">**ActivationAttributes** - Type of activation mechanism that the user is using.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1655">**IsSessionLicensing** – ali je izbran način za aktivacijo računalnika v skupni rabi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1655">**IsSessionLicensing** – Whether we are currently running under shared computer activation mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1656">**LicenseCategory** – kategorija Officeove licence, ki jo uporabnik uporablja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1656">**LicenseCategory** – Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1657">**Licenses** – seznam imen vseh Officeovih licenc, ki so bile zaznane v računalniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1657">**Licenses** – List of names of all the  Office licenses that are present on the machine</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1658">**LicenseStatuses** – stanje vseh Officeovih licenc, ki so bile zaznane v računalniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1658">**LicenseStatuses** – Status of all the Office licenses present on the machine</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensinggetentitlement"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1659">Office.Licensing.GetEntitlement</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1659">Office.Licensing.GetEntitlement</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1660">Te podatke zberemo, ko uporabnik nastavi napravo in pokličemo storitev licenciranja, da zazna, ali je prijavljeni uporabnik upravičen do Officea ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1660">We collect this when the user is setting up a device and we call our licensing service to detect if the logged in user has an Office entitlement or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1661">Da dogodek vrne rezultat klica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1661">This reports the result of that call.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1662">Dogodek je pomemben pri zaznavanju, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju in nima omogočene vse funkcionalnosti; uporabljajo se za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1662">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1663">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1663">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1664">**EntitlementCount** – število upravičenosti, ki jih je uporabnik</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1664">**EntitlementCount** – Number of entitlements the user has</span></span>


### <a name="officelicensingheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1665">Office.Licensing.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1665">Office.Licensing.Heartbeat</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1666">Za vsako sejo preverimo, ali je minilo 72 ur od zadnje obnovitve licence, in poskušamo podaljšati potek trenutne licence.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1666">On every session we check if 72 hours have passed since the last license renewal and try to extend the expiry of the current license.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1667">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo, ali je bil klic uspešen ali neuspešen, da lahko podaljšamo potek licence in omogočimo funkcionalnost Officea, ki ga je namestil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1667">This event reports the success or failure of the call that we make to ensure we can extend the expiry of the license and keep the user's Office installation functional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1668">Pri diagnosticiranju težav, povezanih z naročnino, in težav storitev je ta dogodek ključen za uporabnika in pri zaznavanju regresij za že aktitivrane uporabnike naročnine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1668">It is critical in diagnosing subscription related issues and service issues for the user and is critical in detecting regressions for already activated subscription users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1669">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1669">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1670">**Mode** – predstavitev orodja za oštevilčenje zbirke za licenciranje Officea, ki se uporablja v tem računalniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1670">**Mode** – An enumerator representation of the Office licensing stack that is being used on this machine</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensinginclientpinredemptioncallpinredemptionapi"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1671">Office.Licensing.InClientPinRedemption.CallPinRedemptionAPI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1671">Office.Licensing.InClientPinRedemption.CallPinRedemptionAPI</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1672">V tej telemetriji so prikazani rezultati klicne storitve za prevzem PIN-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1672">This telemetry tracks the results of Office's pin redemption service call.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1673">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1673">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1674">**ClientTransactionId** – Enolični identifikator za klic storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1674">**ClientTransactionId** - Unique identifier for the service call.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1675">**ErrorCategory** – vsaka vrsta napake lahko pade v kategorijo »bolj splošna«, na primer »vnovičen poskus«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1675">**ErrorCategory** - Each error type can fall into a more general category, such as "Retryable".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1676">**ErrorType** – vzrok neuspeha, na primer »AlreadyRedeemedByOther«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1676">**ErrorType** - Reason of failure, such as "AlreadyRedeemedByOther".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1677">**InAFOFlow** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali smo v toku AFO redemption.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1677">**InAFOFlow** - A Boolean indicating if we are in the AFO redemption flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1678">**StatusCode** – rezultat klica storitve z eno besedo, na primer »ustvarjeno«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1678">**StatusCode** - One-word result of the service call, such as "Created".</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingofficeclientlicensingdolicensevalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1750">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1750">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1751">Predstavlja metapodatke za licenciranje, ki se pridobijo iz naprave ob vsakem zagonu, in iz katerih so razvidni identifikator licence, stanje licence, vrsta in druge lastnosti licence. Ti parametri so pomembni pri prepoznavanju nabora funkcij, ki so na voljo za uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1751">This is licensing metadata that is collected from the device on every boot that reports the license acid, license status, type and other properties of the license that are critical in identifying the features set available to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1752">To je zelo pomembno pri prepoznavanju nabora funkcij, ki so na voljo za uporabnika, in ali uporabnik morda ni deležen nekatere funkcionalnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1752">This is critical in identifying the feature set available to the user and if any functionality is missing for the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1753">Ta dogodek se prav tako uporablja za izračune dnevnih aktivnih uporabnikov/mesečnih aktivnih uporabnikov in za druga poročila, ki jih ustvarjajo različne skupine v Officeu, saj je iz njih razvidna vrsta izdelka, ki ga uporablja uporabnik, ali gre za naročniški izdelek in ali je za uporabnike morda onemogočena določena funkcionalnost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1753">It is also used for Daily active users/Monthly active user calculations and various other reports by various teams across Office as this tells the type product that the user is using, whether it is a subscription product and whether they are missing any critical functionality.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1754">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1754">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1755">**FullValidationMode** – način, ki označuje, da je preverjanje veljavnosti licence v načinu polnega preverjanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1755">**FullValidationMode** – Mode indicating that we are in full validation of license verification</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1756">**IsRFM** – označuje, ali je za uporabnika izbran način zmanjšane funkcionalnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1756">**IsRFM** – Indicates whether the user is in reduced functionality mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1757">**IsSCA** – označuje, ali smo izbrali način za aktivacijo računalnika v skupni rabi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1757">**IsSCA** – Indicates whether we are running in Shared computer activation mode</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1758">**IsSubscription** – označuje, ali uporabnik uporablja naročniško licenco</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1758">**IsSubscription** – Indicates whether the user is using a subscription license or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1759">**IsvNext** – označuje, ali uporabljamo novo sodobno zbirko za licenciranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1759">**IsvNext** – Indicates whether we are using the new modern licensing stack or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1760">**LicenseCategory** – kategorija Officeove licence, ki jo uporabnik uporablja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1760">**LicenseCategory** - Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1761">**LicenseStatus** – stanje Officeove licence, ki jo uporabnik uporablja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1761">**LicenseStatus** – Status of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1762">**LicenseType** – kategorija Officeove licence, ki jo uporabnik uporablja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1762">**LicenseType** - Type of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1763">**LicensingACID** – identifikator GUID, ki predstavlja Officeov izdelek, za katerega je uporabnik prejel licenco</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1763">**LicensingACID** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1764">**OlsLicenseId** – alfanumerični identifikator licence, ki je bil izdan za uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1764">**OlsLicenseId** - An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1765">**SkuIdIsNull** – označuje, ali smo naleteli na težavo, in ne poznamo izdelka, ki ga uporabnik uporablja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1765">**SkuIdIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered an error and don't know the product that the user is running</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1766">**SlapiIsNull** – označuje, ali smo naleteli na težavo pri naseljevanju enega od predmetov licenciranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1766">**SlapiIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered a problem in populating one of the licensing objects</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensingonlinerepair"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1767">Office.Licensing.OnlineRepair</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1767">Office.Licensing.OnlineRepair</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1768">Ta dogodek se aktivira, če iz neznanega razloga ne uspemo aktivirati uporabnika in mu moramo prikazati pogovorno okno, naj obišče spletno mesto pomoči in poskuša izvesti korake za odpravljanje težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1768">If we are not able to activate a user for some reason and have to show them a dialog that asks them to go online and try repair steps, this event is fired.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1769">Dogodki so pomembni pri zaznavanju, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju in ima omogočeno vso funkcionalnost, se uporabljajo za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1769">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1770">Ta dogodek ne zbere nobenega polja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1770">This event collects no fields.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingoobetrybuychoice"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1771">Office.Licensing.OOBE.TryBuyChoice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1771">Office.Licensing.OOBE.TryBuyChoice</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1772">Uporabniki z vnaprej nameščenim sistemom Office v novih računalnikih, ki nimajo pravice do Officea, so prikazani v pogovornem oknu, s katerim lahko preskusite, kupite ali vnesete ključ izdelka, da dobi licenco.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1772">Users with pre-installed Office on new machines who have no Office entitlement are shown a dialog through which they can try, buy or enter a product key to get licensed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1773">Ta dogodek zajame dejanje uporabnika v pogovornem oknu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1773">This event captures the user action on the dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1774">Ta dogodek se uporablja za spremljanje dejanja uporabnika, ki se prikaže v pogovornem oknu, ki je prikazano uporabnikom brez pravic za Office, v katerem je bil Office vnaprej nameščen v računalniku, in pomaga ugotoviti, ali je uporabnik licenciral ali ga ni licenciral z načrtom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1774">This event is used to track the user action taken on the dialog shown to users with no Office entitlement where Office was pre-installed on the machine and helps determining if the user is licensed or unlicensed by design.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1775">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1775">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1776">**Nakup** – pove, ali je uporabnik kliknil gumb »kupi« ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1776">**Buy** - Tells if the user clicked on the buy button or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1777">**ForceAutoActivate** – pove, ali želite aktivirati aktiviranje v aplikaciji ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1777">**ForceAutoActivate** - Tells if in-app activation should be attempted or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1778">**GoBackToSignIn** – pove, ali se je uporabnik želel znova vpisati (po možnosti z drugim računom)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1778">**GoBackToSignIn** - Tells if the user wanted to sign in again (possibly with another account)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1779">**IsPin** – pove, ali je uporabnik vnesel kodo PIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1779">**IsPin** - Tells if the user entered a pin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1780">**Productkey** – pove, ali je uporabnik poskusil vnesti ključ izdelka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1780">**ProductKey** - Tells if the user tried to enter a product key</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1781">**Preskusite** – pove, ali je uporabnik kliknil gumb »poskusi« ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1781">**Try** - Tells if the user clicked on the try button or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1782">**UserDismissed** – to pove, ali je uporabnik zavrnil pogovorno okno in je bil torej v načinu »Grace« ali »zmanjšanem načinu«, ker se ni odločil kupiti Office ali dobiti preskusne različice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1782">**UserDismissed** - This tells if the user dismissed the dialog and thus would be in grace or reduced functionality mode because they didn't choose to buy office or get a trial</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingpurchase"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1783">Office.Licensing.Purchase</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1783">Office.Licensing.Purchase</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1784">*[Ta dogodek je bil odstranjen iz trenutnih graditev Officea, vendar se bo morda še vedo pojavljal v starejših graditvah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1784">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1785">Preskus, s katerim uporabniku omogočimo samodejno plačevanje za Office neposredno iz aplikacije, ne da bi za to moral zapreti aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1785">We have an experiment that gives the user an option to try and setup autopay for Office directly from an app without ever leaving the context of the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1786">Ta dogodek ponazarja uspešnost ali neuspešnost poskusa skupaj s kodo napake.
