<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1787">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1787">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1788">**StorePurchaseStatus** – predstavlja kodo napake/kodo uspeha za klic nakupa, ki je bil izveden prek Trgovine Windows</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1788">**StorePurchaseStatus** – Represents the error code/success code of the purchase call that was made through windows store</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingsearchforsessiontoken"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1789">Office.Licensing.SearchForSessionToken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1789">Office.Licensing.SearchForSessionToken</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1790">Če je uporabnik izbral način za aktivacijo računalnika v skupni rabi, v računalniku poskušamo poiskati žeton seje, ki uporabniku omogoča uporabo aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1790">If the user is running under shared computer activation mode, we try to search for a session token on the machine which allows the user to use the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1791">Ta dogodek ponazarja scenarij uspešnosti ali neuspešnosti licenciranja skupaj s kodo napake. Dogodki so pomembni pri zaznavanju, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju in ima omogočeno vso funkcionalnost, se uporabljajo za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1791">This event reports the success or failure of the scenario along with the error code It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1792">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1792">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1793">**LoadLicenseResult** – predstavlja kodo napake/kodo uspeha, ali smo lahko naložili licence za trenutnega uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1793">**LoadLicenseResult** – Represents the error code/success code of whether we were able to load the licenses for the current user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1794">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – ponazarja, ali smo poskušali obnoviti žeton za sejo uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1794">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates whether we attempted to renew the user's session token opportunistically</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1795">**SetAcidResult** – predstavlja kodo napake/kodo uspeha, ali smo identifikator lahko nastavili na pričakovano vrednost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1795">**SetAcidResult** – Represent the error code/success code of whether we were able to set the acid to the expected value</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingshownewdeviceactivationdialog"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1796">Office.Licensing.ShowNewDeviceActivationDialog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1796">Office.Licensing.ShowNewDeviceActivationDialog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1797">Ob prvem zagonu Officeove aplikacije bomo poskušali prikazati pogovorno okno za vpis z vnaprej izpolnjenimi poverilnicami, ki jih je uporabnik vnesel za prenos Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1797">On the first boot of an Office app, we will try to show a sign in dialog pre-populated with the credentials the user employed to download Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1798">Uporabnik lahko nato nadaljuje vpis s temi poverilnicami, uporabi druge poverilnice ali prezre pogovorno okno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1798">The user can then continue to sign-in with those credentials, use different credentials or dismiss the dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1799">Ta dogodek poroča o dejanju uporabnika ob prikazu tega pogovornega okna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1799">This event reports the action taken by the user when presented with this dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1800">Dogodki se uporabljajo za zaznavanje, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju sodobne zbirke za licenciranje, za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1800">It is critical for detecting if a user is in a good state on the modern licensing stack, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1801">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1801">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1802">**UserAction** – identifikator za dejanje, ki ga izvede uporabnik, ko se prikaže pogovorno okno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1802">**UserAction** – Identifier for the action taken by the user when presented with the dialog.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingskutoskuconversion"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1803">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1803">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1804">Če moramo v sklopu licenciranja uporabnika spremeniti inventarno številko uporabnika, posredujemo ta signal skupaj s kodo uspeha oziroma neuspeha.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1804">As part of licensing the user, if we have to change the user's SKU from one SKU to another, we send this signal out along with the success or failure code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1805">Dogodek je pomemben pri zaznavanju, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju in nima omogočene vse funkcionalnosti; uporabljajo se za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1805">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1806">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1806">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1807">**DestinationSku** – ime inventarne številke, v katerega se bo pretvoril trenutno nameščeni izdelek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1807">**DestinationSku** – Name of the SKU to which the currently installed product should be converted to</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1808">**PendingAcid** – ID izdelka, za katerega je na čakanju pretvorba inventarne številke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1808">**PendingAcid** – ID of the product for which a SKU conversion is pending</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1809">**SourceSku** – ime izvirne inventarne številke, ki je bila nameščena v računalniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1809">**SourceSku** – Name of the original SKU that was installed on the machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1810">**UninstallProduct** – označuje, ali bo star izdelek odstranjen v sklopu pretvorbe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1810">**UninstallProduct** – Indicates whether the old product will be uninstalled as part of the conversion</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowolsresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1811">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.OLSResults</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1811">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.OLSResults</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1812">Če uporabnik ni licenciran, ustvarimo več servisnih klicev, da dobimo uporabnika v licenčno državo in aktiviramo njihov Officeov izdelek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1812">When a user is unlicensed, we make several service calls to get the user into a licensed state and to activate their Office product.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1813">Ta dogodek se sproži ob pozivu, da storitev Office Licensing preveri, ali ima uporabnik upravičene pravice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1813">This event gets triggered on calling the Office Licensing Service to check if the user has entitlements.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1814">Ta dogodek se bo uporabil za spremljanje stanja licenciranja uporabnikov, ko boste poklicali storitev licenciranja za Office in stanje Officeovega odjemalca, ko boste poskusili dobiti Office aktiviran.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1814">This event is going to be used to track the user licensing health after calling the Office Licensing Service and the Office Client health after attempting to get Office activated.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1815">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1815">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1816">**EntitlementPickerShown** – pove, ali je imela uporabnik več pravic in če je uporabnik moral ročno izbrati od njih, da dobi licenco</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1816">**EntitlementPickerShown** - Tells if the user had multiple entitlements and if the user had to manually choose from them to get licensed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1817">**GetAuthResult** – pove več o tem, da je stranka morda na primer v storitvi, če je na voljo prazna ključa izdelka iz storitve Office Licensing ali če je bila upravičena do drugega izdelka, ki ga je treba pretvoriti v nov izdelek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1817">**GetAuthResult** - Tells various states the client might be in like if they got an empty product key from the Office Licensing Service or if they were entitled for another product and Office needs to be converted to the new product</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1818">**GetEntitlementsCount** – število upravičenosti, ki jih je uporabnik ima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1818">**GetEntitlementsCount** - Tells the number of entitlements the user has</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1819">**GetEntitlementsSucceeded** – pove, ali je klic v storitev Office Licensing API za pridobitev uporabniških pravic uspel ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1819">**GetEntitlementsSucceeded** - Tells if the call to an Office Licensing Service API to retrieve the user's entitlements succeeded or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1820">**GetKeySucceeded** – pove, ali je klic v storitev Office Licensing API za pridobitev ključa uspel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1820">**GetKeySucceeded** - Tells if the call to an Office Licensing Service API to retrieve a key succeeded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1821">**GetNextUserLicenseResult** – pove, ali je sodobni sklad za licenciranje deloval in če je uporabnik dobil licenco ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1821">**GetNextUserLicenseResult** - Tells if the modern licensing stack was able to work and if the user got licensed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1822">**InstallKeyResult** – pove različne razloge, zakaj je uporabnik morda v slabem stanju, kot je, če aktivacija ni uspela ali če je bila namestitev ključa spodletela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1822">**InstallKeyResult** - Tells various reasons why the user might be in a bad state like if activation failed or the installation of the key failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1823">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** – to je zgolj informativno in pove, ali je bil dogodek dodan v preslikavo upravitelja telemetrijo, ne da bi ga izrecno registrirali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1823">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1824">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileSending** – to je zgolj informativno sporočilo in pove, ali je bilo poskušeno dogodek poslati, ne da bi ga izrecno prijavili v preslikavi upravitelja telemetrijo pred roko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1824">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileSending** - This is just informational and tells if the event was attempted to be sent without explicitly registering for it in the telemetry manager map before hand</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1825">**SentOnDestruction** – to je zgolj informativno in pove, ali je bil dogodek dodan v preslikavo upravitelja telemetrijo in ni bil poslan izrecno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1825">**SentOnDestruction** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map and wasn't sent explicitly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1826">**Oznaka** – uporablja se za štetje, kjer je bil dogodek poslan iz programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1826">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1827">**VerifyEntitlementsResult** – pove več o tem, da je uporabnik lahko v storitvi, ko preveri veljavnost upravičenosti, pridobljeno iz storitve Office Licensing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1827">**VerifyEntitlementsResult** - Tells various states the user might be in after validating the entitlements retrieved from the Office Licensing Service</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowsearchforbindingresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1828">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.SearchForBindingResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1828">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.SearchForBindingResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1829">Izvirni izdelovalci opreme prodajajo naprave, ki so vključene v Office (celoletne naročnine ali večne).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1829">OEMs sell machines that come with Office (one-year subscriptions or perpetual).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1830">Te Officeove izdelke plačate, ko stranka kupi svoj računalnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1830">These Office products are paid for when the customer purchases their machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1831">Naprave, ki so nastavljene z določenim regkey (OOBEMode: OEMTA), so morda povezane z Officeovo vezavo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1831">Machines that are setup with a specific regkey (OOBEMode: OEMTA) might have an Office binding associated with it.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1832">Ko zaženemo Office v teh napravah, izvajamo storitvene preverbe, ali je najdena Officeovo vezava, ki ustreza računalniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1832">When we boot Office on such machines, we perform service checks to see if an Office binding corresponding to the machine is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1833">Ta dejavnost telemetrijo sledi napakam pri uspehu in napaki pri iskanju vezave, tako da lahko zagotovimo, da lahko naprave, ki imajo zavezujočo vezavo, uspešno pridobivajo in da so naše storitve zdrave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1833">This telemetry activity tracks the success and failure points in searching for a binding so that we can ensure that machines that do have a binding can successfully fetch them, and that our services are healthy.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1834">Ta dejavnost ne sledi strojem, ki so na voljo, da ne bi imeli nobenih vezi z njimi, ko jih preverimo z našimi storitvami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1834">This activity does not track machines that turn out to not have any bindings associated with them after we check with our services.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1835">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1835">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1836">**DexShouldRetry** – znak, da smo pripravili težavo, ki jo je mogoče odpraviti (Internet ali strežniki niso na voljo)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1836">**DexShouldRetry** - Signal that we’ve hit a retryable issue (no internet or servers are down)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1837">**GenuineTicketFailure** – nam pove napako HRESULT, ko poskušate dobiti računalnik s sistemom Windows pristno vstopnico/ključ izdelka (WPK).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1837">**GenuineTicketFailure** - Tells us the failure HRESULT when trying to get the machine's Windows genuine ticket/product key (WPK).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1838">**PinValidationFailure** – nam pove, zakaj ni uspelo izvesti postopka preverjanja pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1838">**PinValidationFailure** - Tells us why the pin validation process failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1839">Morebitne napake so:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1839">Possible errors:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1840">GeoBlocked</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1840">GeoBlocked</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1841">InvalidFormat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1841">InvalidFormat</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1842">InvalidPin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1842">InvalidPin</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1843">InvalidState</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1843">InvalidState</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1844">InvalidVersion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1844">InvalidVersion</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1845">Neznano</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1845">Unknown</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1846">Uporablja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1846">Used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1847">**PinValidationResult** – pove nam, kaj je rezultat preverjanja pristnosti kode PIN, ki je ni bilo mogoče razvozlati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1847">**PinValidationResult** - Tells us the pin validation result of a pin that we failed to crack.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1848">**Pkpn** – Pkpn obseg, za katerega pripada koda PIN.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1848">**Pkpn** - The pkpn range that the pin belongs to.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1849">**Uspeh** – pomeni, da smo uspešno pridobivali veljavno Officeovo vezavo (PIN) za napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1849">**Success** - Indicates that we successfully fetched a valid Office binding (pin) for the machine.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1850">**Tag** – pove nam, na kateri stopnji smo nehali iskati vezavo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1850">**Tag** - Tells us at which step we stopped searching for a binding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1851">Možna oznaka:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1851">Possible tags:</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1852">0x03113809 – med preverjanjem kode PIN napaka ni interneta/storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1852">0x03113809    No internet/service error while validating pin</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1853">0x0311380a – napaka pri preverjanju PIN, poslano s poljem »PinValidationFailure«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1853">0x0311380a    Pin validation failure, sent with PinValidationFailure field</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1854">0x0310410f – uspeh, poslano s poljem »uspeh«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1854">0x0310410f    Success, sent with Success field</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1855">0x0311380d – vnovične napake (težave z internetom, neznane napake)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1855">0x0311380d    Retry-able errors (internet issues, unknown errors)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1856">0x0311380e – napake, ki se ne dajo ponoviti (ponudba za vezavo je potekla)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1856">0x0311380e    Non-retry-able errors (binding offer expired)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1857">0x0311380f – druge napake (ki jih ni mogoče licencirati)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1857">0x0311380f    Other errors (unable to license)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1858">0x03104111 – ni uspelo razvozlati Officeovega pina, poslanega z poljem» PinValidationResult «.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1858">0x03104111    Failed to crack the Office pin, sent with PinValidationResult field</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1859">**WpkBindingFailure** – pove napako, da je koda napake pridobila kodo PIN za Office, ki je povezana z WPK računalnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1859">**WpkBindingFailure** - Tells us the error code of getting the Office pin bound to the machine's WPK.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowshowafodialogs"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1860">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowAFODialogs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1860">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowAFODialogs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1861">Ko ste uspešno dokončali veljaven Officeov PIN, ki je vezan na računalnik, ki je bil vnaprej povezan s sistemom Office, je uporabnik v pogovornem oknu za vpis ali v pogovorno okno za prevzem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1861">After successfully obtaining a valid Office pin bound to a machine pre-bundled with Office, we show the user either a sign-in dialog or a redemption dialog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1862">Ko je koda PIN preplačana, je prikazano pogovorno okno »EULA«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1862">Once the pin is redeemed, we show the EULA dialog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1863">Kot del naše funkcije modernizacije AFO smo osvežili dve pogovorni okni, da bi posredovali več informacij o Officeovem izdelku, ki je na voljo v računalniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1863">As a part of our modernizing AFO feature, we refreshed the two dialogs to convey more information regarding the Office product that comes with the machine.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1864">Ta telemetrijo je namenjena sledenju, če naša funkcija uspešno zmanjša število uporabnikov, pri čemer prevzame njihov izdelek tako, da spremlja potek in izstopne točke postopka prevzema (ki je bil opuščen).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1864">This telemetry is to track if our feature successfully reduces user friction in redeeming their product by tracking the flow and exit points of the redemption process (which dialog was dismissed).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1865">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1865">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1866">**ActionActivate** – znak, da je uporabnik kliknil gumb »Aktiviraj«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1866">**ActionActivate** - Signal that user clicked the “Activate” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1867">**ActionChangeAccount** – znak, da je uporabnik kliknil hiperpovezavo »uporabi drug račun«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1867">**ActionChangeAccount** -  Signal that user clicked the “Use a different account” hyperlink.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1868">**ActionCreateAccount** – znak, da je uporabnik kliknil gumb »Ustvari račun«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1868">**ActionCreateAccount** - Signal that user clicked the “Create account” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1869">**ActionSignIn** – signal, ki ga je uporabnik kliknil z gumbom »vpis«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1869">**ActionSignIn** - Signal that user clicked the “Sign in” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1870">**CurrentView** – vrsto pogovornega okna, ki ga je uporabnik zaprl.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1870">**CurrentView** - The type of dialog the user closed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1871">**DialogEULA** – signal, da smo prikazali pogovorno okno »Sprejmi EULA«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1871">**DialogEULA** -  Signal that we showed the ‘Accept EULA’ dialog.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1872">**DialogRedemption** – signal, ki smo ga pokazali v pogovornem oknu »AFO ' Redemption«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1872">**DialogRedemption** - Signal that we showed the AFO redemption dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1873">**DialogSignIn** – signal, da smo prikazali pogovorno okno za vpis v AFO '.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1873">**DialogSignIn** - Signal that we showed the AFO sign-in dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1874">**EmptyRedemptionDefaults** – sporočilo, da ni bilo mogoče pridobivati privzetih informacij o prevzemu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1874">**EmptyRedemptionDefaults** - Signal that we failed to fetch default redemption information.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1875">**GetRedemptionInfo** – znak, da pridobivamo demografske informacije za prevzem PIN.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1875">**GetRedemptionInfo** - Signal that we’re fetching demographic information for pin redemption.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1876">**MalformedCountryCode** – znak, da je koda države, ki jo potrebujete za prevzem PIN-a, popačena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1876">**MalformedCountryCode** - Signal that the country code needed for pin redemption is malformed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1877">**OExDetails** – podrobnosti o napaki, ki se prikaže, ko je bil v pogovornem oknu »vpis identitete« opuščen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1877">**OExDetails** - The error details we get back when identity's sign-in dialog was dismissed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1878">**OExType** – podrobnosti o napaki, ki se prikaže, ko je bil v pogovornem oknu »vpis identitete« opuščen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1878">**OExType** - The error type we get back when identity's sign-in dialog was dismissed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1879">**Tag** – pove nam, s katerim korakom uporabnik zapusti proces prevzema AFO '.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1879">**Tag** - Tells us at which step the user exits the AFO redemption process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1880">Možna oznaka:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1880">Possible tags:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1881">0x0311380b – uporabnik je opustil pogovornega okno »prevzem identitete« iz pogovornega okna »redemption«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1881">0x0311380b    User dismissed identity's sign-in dialog from redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1882">0x0311380c – ni uspel samodejnega nalaganja identitete po vpisu uporabnika iz pogovornega okna »redemption«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1882">0x0311380c    Failed to auto-load an identity post user sign-in from redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1883">0x03113810 – ni uspel naložiti demografskih informacij kupca (koda države, jezik, valuta, ponudba za preskusno različico in nastavitve marketinga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1883">0x03113810    Failed to load the account's demographic information (country code, language,     currency, trial offer, and marketing preferences)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1884">0x03113805 – uporabnik je opustil pogovornega okno »prevzem identitete« iz pogovornega okna »redemption«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1884">0x03113805    User dismissed identity's sign-in dialog from sign-in dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1885">0x03113806 ni uspel samodejnega nalaganja identitete po vpisu uporabnika iz pogovornega okna »vpis«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1885">0x03113806    Failed to auto-load an identity post user sign-in from sign-in dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1886">0x03113807 ni uspel samodejno naložiti identitete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1886">0x03113807    Failed to auto-load an identity</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1887">0x03113811 uporabnik  je zaprl pogovorno okno za vpis/prevzem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1887">0x03113811    User closed the sign-in/redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1888">0x03113812 uporabnik je zaprl pogovorno okno Sprejmi EULA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1888">0x03113812    User closed the accept EULA dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1889">0x03113808 uporabnik je sprejel EULA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1889">0x03113808    User accepted the EULA</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1890">Uporabnik 0x03113811 je zaprl pogovorno okno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1890">0x03113811      User closed a dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1891">Uporabnik 0x2370e3a0 je zaprl pogovorno okno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1891">0x2370e3a0      User closed a dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1892">0x2370e3c1 obiščite spletno mesto za prevzem PIN-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1892">0x2370e3c1      Go to web for pin redemption</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1893">0x2370e3a1 obiščite spletno mesto za prevzem PIN-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1893">0x2370e3a1      Go to web for pin redemption</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1894">Pogovorno okno »0x2370e3c0 zaporedje«, ki ga je povzročil uporabnik, ki je bil na tekočem v pogovornem oknu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1894">0x2370e3c0      Dialog sequence looped caused by user going back and forth in the dialog flow</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1895">Uporabnik 0x2370e3a3 je kliknil hiperpovezavo »not Now«, ki preskoči ponudbo za AFO ' za to sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1895">0x2370e3a3      User clicked “Not now” hyperlink which skips the AFO offer for that session</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1896">Uporabnik 0x2370e3a2 je kliknil »nikoli mi ne kaži več« hiperpovezave, ki onemogoči ponudbo za AFO '</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1896">0x2370e3a2      User clicked on “Never show this to me” hyperlink which disables the AFO offer</span></span>


- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1897">**UseInAppRedemption** – nam pove, ali imamo uporabniki v aplikaciji za prevzem ali pa jih pošljejo v splet, da bodo lahko izkoristili pogosto kodo PIN (vnaprej izpolnjene).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1897">**UseInAppRedemption** - Tells us if we're keeping users in-app for redemption or sending them to the web to redeem their fetched pin (pre-populated).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1898">**UseModernAFO** – nam pove, ali uporabljate novo ali staro AFO
 izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1898">**UseModernAFO** - Tells us if we're using the new or old AFO experience.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowshowtrybuydialogforoobe"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1899">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowTryBuyDialogForOOBE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1899">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowTryBuyDialogForOOBE</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1900">Ko imajo novi računalniki vnaprej nameščeno različico sistema Office in uporabnik nima upravičene osebe, se prikaže pogovorno okno, v katerem je uporabniku na voljo možnost, da preizkusite, kupite ali vnesete ključ izdelka, tako da lahko uporabnik pridobi licenco in ta dogodek sledi, če je prikazano pogovorno okno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1900">When new machines have Office pre-installed and the user doesn't have an entitlement we show a dialog which gives the user the option to try, buy or enter a product key so that the user can get licensed and this event tracks if the dialog was shown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1901">Ta dogodek vam bo pomagal pri zavedanju, ali je bil pogovor v pogovornem oknu uporabniku prikazan, če želite preskusiti, kupiti ali vnesti ključ izdelka, zato nam bo pomagal ugotoviti, ali je uporabnik imel možnost pridobiti licenco.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1901">This event will help with knowing if the dialog was shown to the user to try, buy or enter the product key and hence will help us determine if the user had the opportunity to get licensed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1902">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1902">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1903">**ActiveView** – pove ID pogovornega okna, ki je prikazan uporabniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1903">**ActiveView** - Tells the dialog ID shown to the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1904">**CurrentOOBEMode** – pove način prednamestitve (način OOBE, kot je AFO ', OEM itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1904">**CurrentOOBEMode** - Tells the pre-install mode (OOBE mode such as AFO, OEM etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1905">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** – to je zgolj informativno in pove, ali je bil dogodek dodan v preslikavo upravitelja telemetrijo, ne da bi ga izrecno registrirali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1905">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1906">**SentOnDestruction** – to je zgolj informativno in pove, ali je bil dogodek dodan v preslikavo upravitelja telemetrijo in ni bil poslan izrecno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1906">**SentOnDestruction** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map and wasn't sent explicitly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1907">**ShowTryButton** – pove, ali je uporabnik v pogovornem oknu prikazal gumb »poskusi« ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1907">**ShowTryButton** - Tells if the Try Button was shown to the user on the dialog or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1908">**Oznaka** – uporablja se za štetje, kjer je bil dogodek poslan iz programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1908">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowtrialflow"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1909">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.TrialFlow</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1909">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.TrialFlow</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1910">Če uporabnik, ki je bil vnaprej nameščen v računalniku, ne dobi licence, poskuša dobiti preskusno različico, se ta dogodek sproži.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1910">When an unlicensed user of Office pre-installed on a machine is attempting to get a trial, this event gets triggered.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1911">Uporablja se, da si ogledate, s katero potjo bo uporabnik dobil preskusno različico, in če bo prišlo do kakršnih koli napak pri pridobivanju preskusne različice z nakupi v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1911">It is used to see which path the user would follow to get a trial and if there were any errors while getting the trial through in-app purchases.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1912">Odvisno od dejanja uporabnika in rezultata nakupa aplikacije v storitvi, lahko uporabnik na koncu ne bo licenciral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1912">Depending on the user action and the result of the in-app purchase the user could end up being unlicensed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1913">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1913">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1914">**HasConnectivity** – pove, ali ima uporabnik internetno povezljivost, v primeru, da uporabnik morda ne bo rabil licence milosti za pet dni ali pa je morda v načinu zmanjšane funkcionalnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1914">**HasConnectivity** - Tells if the user has internet connectivity and in case there isn't the user might have to use a grace license for five days or may be in reduced functionality mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1915">**InAppTrialPurchase** – pove, ali je polet omogočen za začetek nakupa SDK nakup v trgovini za zajem PI in nakup preskusne različice znotraj programa *[to polje je bilo odstranjeno iz tekočih različic Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših različicah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1915">**InAppTrialPurchase** - Tells if the flight is enabled for launching the Store Purchase SDK to capture PI and purchase a trial from within the application *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1916">**IsRS1OrGreater** – pove, ali je različica OS večja od RS1 ali ne, saj bi moral biti nakup v trgovini SDK že uporabljen samo, če je različica OS večja, kot je RS1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1916">**IsRS1OrGreater** - Tells if the OS Version is greater than RS1 or not since the Store Purchase SDK should be used only if the OS Version is greater that RS1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1917">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** – to je zgolj informativno in pove, ali je bil dogodek dodan v preslikavo upravitelja telemetrijo, ne da bi ga izrecno registrirali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1917">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding**: This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1918">**OEMSendToWebForTrial** – pove, ali je polet omogočen za pošiljanje uporabnikov v splet, da izkoristi preskusno različico</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1918">**OEMSendToWebForTrial** - Tells if the flight is enabled to send users to the web to redeem a trial</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1919">**StoreErrorConditions** – pove različne pogoje, v skladu s katerimi je bil nakup SDK shrambe ni uspel *[To polje je bilo odstranjeno iz tekočih različic Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših različicah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1919">**StoreErrorConditions** - Tells the various conditions under which the Store Purchase SDK could have failed *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1920">**StoreErrorHResult** – pove, da je koda napake vrnjena iz trgovine SDK nakup v trgovini *[to polje je bilo odstranjeno iz tekočih različic Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših različicah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1920">**StoreErrorHResult** - Tells the error code returned from the Store Purchase SDK *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1921">**StorePurchaseStatusResult** – pove, da je rezultat klica SDK za nakup v trgovini in če je uporabnik ustvaril nakup ali ne, s katerim lahko ugotovite, ali mora uporabnik dobiti licenco za uporabo sistema Office *[to polje je bilo odstranjeno iz tekočih različic Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno pojavi v starejših različicah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1921">**StorePurchaseStatusResult** - Tells the result of calling the Store Purchase SDK and if the user made a purchase or not which will help determine if the user should get licensed to use Office *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1922">**Oznaka** – uporablja se za štetje, kjer je bil dogodek poslan iz programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1922">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1923">**UserSignedInExplicitly** – pove, ali je uporabnik v tem primeru izrecno vpisan v splet – če je bil uporabljen za preskusno različico *[to polje je bilo odstranjeno iz tekočih različic Officea, vendar je morda še vedno prikazan v starejših različicah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1923">**UserSignedInExplicitly** - Tells if the user signed in explicitly in which case, we would re-direct users to the web for the trial *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingusegracekey"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1924">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1924">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1925">Če iz neznanega razloga nismo uspeli licencirati uporabnika, namestimo ključ za dovoljeno obdobje in pošljemo ta signal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1925">For some reason if we are unable to license the user, we install a grace key and send out this signal that signifies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1926">Dogodek je pomemben pri zaznavanju, ali je uporabnik v dobrem stanju in nima omogočene vse funkcionalnosti; uporabljajo se za stanje sistema in za diagnostične namene, ko uporabnik prijavi težavo z računalnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1926">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1927">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1927">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1928">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – označuje, ali smo priložnostno poskušali obnoviti licenco za uporabnika v način za aktivacijo računalnika v skupni rabi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1928">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates if we attempted an opportunistic renewal for the user in shared computer activation mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1929">**ReArmResult** – označuje rezultat vrnitve v obdobje pred aktiviranjem nameščenega ključa, s katerem je mogoče razširiti trenutno licenco</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1929">**ReArmResult** – Indicates the result of rearming the installed key which can extend the expiry of the current license</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteenrollmentresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1930">OneNote.EnrollmentResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1930">OneNote.EnrollmentResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1931">Ta dogodek zabeleži stanje ob vpisu InTune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1931">This event logs the status upon Intune enrollment.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1932">Ta primer je specifičen za InTune omogočeni računi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1932">This scenario is specific to Intune enabled accounts.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1933">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1933">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1934">**EnrollmentResult** – rezultat vpisa InTune</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1934">**EnrollmentResult** - The result of Intune enrollment</span></span>

## <a name="microsoft-autoupdate-mau-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1935">Dogodki Microsoft autoupdate (MAU)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1935">Microsoft AutoUpdate (MAU) events</span></span>

### <a name="appdelegate_launch"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-1936">appdelegate_launch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1936">appdelegate_launch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1937">Ta dogodek pomeni, da je prišlo do poskusa zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1937">This event denotes that an attempt to launch the app occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1938">Zabeležimo njegov rezultat (neuspeh ali uspeh).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1938">We log its result (failure or success).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1939">S tem dogodkom ugotovimo primere, v katerih MAU ne bo začela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1939">We use this event to identify cases in which MAU fails to launch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-1940">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1940">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1941">**Aplikacija** – postopek prijave, ki pošilja dogodek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1941">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1942">**AppInfo_Language** – jezik, v katerem se izvaja aplikacija v razdelku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1942">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1943">**AppversionLong** – različica programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1943">**AppversionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1944">**Channel** – ugodnost občinstva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1944">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1945">**Device_NetworkCountry** – država/regija naprave (ki temelji na naslovu IP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1945">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1946">**DeviceID** – identifikator naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1946">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1947">**DeviceInfo_Model** – model strojne opreme naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1947">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1948">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – vrsta omrežja (Wi-Fi, žična, neznana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1948">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1949">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – različica operacijskega sistema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1949">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the Operating System</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1950">**Event_ReceivedTime** – ura prejemanja telemetrijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1950">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1951">**EventInfo_Name** – ime telemetričnega dogodka, ki se zabeleži.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1951">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1952">**EventInfo_Time** – čas, ko se je dogodek v dnevniku zgodil</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1952">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1953">**HowTocheck** – ugodnost za preverjanje posodobitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1953">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1954">**Nosilnost** – nabor statičnega besedila, ki označuje stanje izstrelitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1954">**Payload** - A set of static text indicating launch status.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1955">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – država naprava (ki temelji na naslovu IP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1955">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1956">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – prve 3 oktete naslova IP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1956">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1957">**ID** seje – identifikator za sejo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1957">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1965">**Channel** – ugodnost občinstva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1965">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1966">**Device_NetworkCountry** – država/regija naprave (ki temelji na naslovu IP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1966">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1968">**DeviceInfo_Model** – model strojne opreme naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1968">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1969">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – vrsta omrežja (Wi-Fi, žična, neznana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1969">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wifi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1970">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – različica operacijskega sistema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1970">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1972">**EventInfo_Name** – ime telemetričnega dogodka, ki se zabeleži.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1972">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-1973">**EventInfo_Time** – čas, ko se je dogodek v dnevniku zgodil</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-1973">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

### <a name="cloningtask_helpertoolconnection"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-2065">cloningtask_helpertoolconnection</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-2065">cloningtask_helpertoolconnection</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-2066">Ta dogodek zabeleži težave z namestitvijo klona (tj. ne bomo se povezali z pomočnikom, da bi uporabili posodobitev, ali pa vzpostavili povezavo, vendar pomočnik ne more uporabiti posodobitve).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-2066">This event records issues with install on clone (i.e. either we fail to connect to the helper to apply an update, or we connect but the helper is unable to apply the update).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-2067">Če smo zabeležili kartoteko, to pomeni, da ni bilo mogoče namestiti klona in se bo zdaj treba odkupiti posodobitvi na mestu uporabe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-2067">If we ever get a record reported, this means install on clone has failed and will now have to fallback to an in-place update.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-2068">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-2068">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-2069">**Aplikacija** – postopek prijave, ki pošilja dogodek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-2069">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5531">**DeviceID** – identifikator naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5531">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5532">**DeviceInfo_Model** – model strojne opreme naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5532">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5536">**EventInfo_Name** – ime telemetričnega dogodka, ki se zabeleži.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5536">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

## <a name="onenote-sync-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5543">Dogodki sinhronizacije za OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5543">OneNote sync events</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5544">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5544">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5545">Ta dogodek zabeleži rezultat sinhronizacije zvezka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5545">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5546">Uporablja se za prikaz števila enoličnih ciljev sinhronizacije pri izračunavanju rezultata sinhronizacije za OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5546">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5547">Zbrana so naslednja polja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5547">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5548">**CachedError_Code** – oštevilčena ali alfanumerična koda, ki se uporablja za določanje narave predpomnjene napake, in/ali razloga, zakaj se je pojavila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5548">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5549">**CachedError_Description** – opis napake v predpomnilniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5549">**CachedError_Description** – a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5550">**CachedError_Tag** – določite, kje v kodi je shranjena predpomnjena napaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5550">**CachedError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5551">**CachedError_Type** – vrsta predpomnjene napake, na primer Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5551">**CachedError_Type** – the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5552">**ExecutionTime** – čas v milisekundah za repliciranje zvezka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5552">**ExecutionTime** – time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5553">**Gosid** – globalni ID prostora za predmete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5553">**Gosid** – global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5554">**IdentityType** – vrsta identitete, npr. Windows Live, ID org ipd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5554">**IdentityType** – identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5555">**InitialReplicationInSession** – ali je to replikacija prva replikacija zvezka po odprtju ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5555">**InitialReplicationInSession** – is this replication the first notebook replication after open or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5556">**IsBackgroundSync** – ali je to sinhroniziranje ozadja ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5556">**IsBackgroundSync** – is this a background sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5557">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – je predpomnjena napaka, ki jo je mogoče zatreti ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5557">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – is the cached error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5558">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – je predpomnjena napaka, ki je nepričakovana ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5558">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5559">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – je napaka sinhronizacije na ravni zvezka ukinjena ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5559">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5560">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – je napaka sinhronizacije na ravni zvezka nepričakovana ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5560">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5561">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – ali je napaka sinhronizacije odseka ukinjena ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5561">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5562">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – je napaka sinhronizacije odseka nepričakovana ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5562">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5563">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – je sinhronizacija zvezka z moderno vsebino strani sinhronizirana ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5563">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5564">**LastAttemptedSync** – časovni žig, ko je bil zvezek poskusil sinhronizirati nazadnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5564">**LastAttemptedSync** – timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5565">**LastBackgroundSync** – časovni žig, ko je bil izveden zadnji sinhronizacijo v ozadju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5565">**LastBackgroundSync** – timestamp when the latest background sync was attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5566">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – datum, ko je bil zvezek nazadnje gledan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5566">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – the date when the notebook was last viewed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5567">**LastSuccessfulSync** – časovni žig, ko je bil zvezek uspešno sinhroniziran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5567">**LastSuccessfulSync** – timestamp when the notebook successfully synced before</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5568">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – ali mora biti sinhronizacija znova zagnana zaradi neskladij ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5568">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync need to restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5569">**NotebookErrorCode** – koda napake sinhronizacije na ravni zvezek, ki je shranjena v prostoru zvezek Graph</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5569">**NotebookErrorCode** – notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5570">**NotebookId** – ID zvezka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5570">**NotebookId** – notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5571">**NotebookType** – vrsta zvezka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5571">**NotebookType** – notebook type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5572">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – ali ponovni zagon sinhronizacije zaradi neskladij ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5572">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5573">**SectionError_Code** – oštevilčena ali alfanumerična koda, ki se uporablja za določanje narave napake sinhronizacije odseka in/ali razloga, zakaj se je pojavila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5573">**SectionError_Code** – a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the section sync error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5574">**SectionError_Description** – opis napake sinhronizacije odseka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5574">**SectionError_Description** – a description of the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5575">**SectionError_Tag** – določite mesto, kjer v kodi je sporočilo o napaki sinhronizacije odseka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5575">**SectionError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5576">**SectionError_Type** – vrsta napake sinhronizacije odseka, npr. Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5576">**SectionError_Type** – the type of the section sync error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5577">**Uspeh** – ali je sinhronizacija zvezka uspešna ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5577">**Success** – is the notebook sync successful or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5578">**SyncDestinationType** – vrsta ciljne sinhronizacije, tj. OneDrive ali SharePoint online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5578">**SyncDestinationType** – sync destination type, i.e. OneDrive or SharePoint Online</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5579">**SyncId** – številka, ki je enolična za vsako sinhronizacijo zvezka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5579">**SyncId** – a number unique to each notebook sync</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5580">**SyncWasFirstInSession** – ali je sinhronizirana prva sinhronizacija v trenutni seji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5580">**SyncWasFirstInSession** – is this sync the first sync in current session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5581">**SyncWasUserInitiated** – ali je ta uporabnik za sinhronizacijo zagnal ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5581">**SyncWasUserInitiated** – is this sync user initiated or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5582">**TenantId** – ID najemnika za SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5582">**TenantId** – SharePoint tenant ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5583">**TimeSinceLastAttemptedSync** – ura od zadnjega poskusa sinhronizacije zvezka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5583">**TimeSinceLastAttemptedSync** – time since last notebook sync attempt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5584">**TimeSinceLastSuccessfulSync** – ura odkar je bila nazadnje uspešna sinhronizacija zvezka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5584">**TimeSinceLastSuccessfulSync** – time since last successful notebook sync</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragerealtimewebsocketsessioninfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5585">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5585">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5586">Ta dogodek prijavi rezultate sinhronizacije za sinhronizacijo spletne vtičnice za tako vsebino programa OneNote moderne sinhronizacije Uporablja se za prikaz števila enoličnih ciljev sinhronizacije pri izračunavanju rezultata sinhronizacije za OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5586">This event logs WebSocket sync result for both OneNote modern page content sync modern hierarchy sync. It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5587">Uporablja se tudi za sodobno delovanje nadzorne plošče za sinhronizacijo programa OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5587">It is also used for OneNote modern sync performance dashboard.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5588">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5588">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5589">**Vzrok** za CloseReason – bližnjica, npr. neobičajno zapiranje itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5589">**CloseReason** - WebSocket close reason, e.g. Abnormal close, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5590">**DataIsFreshCount** – število uspešnih zahtev za vlečenje v srečanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5590">**DataIsFreshCount** - number of successful pull requests in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5591">**ID** seje DeviceSessionId – naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5591">**DeviceSessionId** - Device session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5592">**DownloadCount** – število prenosov v seji »samopostrežna vtičnica«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5592">**DownloadCount** - number of downloads in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5593">**Napaka** – je v osnovi Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5593">**Error** - is basically Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5594">**Exception_Code** – oštevilčena ali alfanumerična koda, ki se uporablja za določanje narave napake, in/ali razloga, zakaj se je pojavila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5594">**Exception_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5595">**Exception_Description** – opis napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5595">**Exception_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5596">**Exception_Tag** – določite, kje v kodi je sporočilo o napaki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5596">**Exception_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5654">**Error_Type** – vrsta napake, npr. Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5654">**Error_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteappprovisioningmovelocalnotebooktoonlinenotebookfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5665">OneNote.App.Omogočanje uporabe.MoveLocalNotebookToOnlineNotebookFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5665">OneNote.App.Provisioning.MoveLocalNotebookToOnlineNotebookFailed</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5666">Ta dogodek se zabeleži ob selitvi lokalnega zvezka na pogon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5666">This event is logged when move of local notebook to drive fails.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5667">Ta primer je specifičen za enotno prijavo uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5667">This scenario is specific to delayed sign-in user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5668">Ko se uporabnik prijavi, je njihov lokalni zvezek prenesen v OneDrive shrambo storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5668">When the user signs-in, their local notebook is transferred to their OneDrive storage.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5669">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5669">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5670">**ErrorMsg** – sporočilo o napaki, ki ustreza napaki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5670">**ErrorMsg** - The error message corresponding to the failure.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestorageconnectivitychanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5671">OneNote.Storage.ConnectivityChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5671">OneNote.Storage.ConnectivityChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5672">Dnevnike dogodkov, če ima uporabnik internetno povezljivost ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5672">The event logs if a user has internet connectivity or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5673">S tem se lahko poveže druge metrike učinkovitosti delovanja zdravja, tako da prezremo dogodke, do katerih pride, ko uporabnik nima internetne povezljivosti, saj ne pričakujemo, da bo zakasnitev vaše storitve sprejemljiva brez internetne povezljivosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5673">This is used to correlate the other sync health performance metrics by allowing us to ignore events that occur while a user does not have internet connectivity as we do not expect our service latency to be acceptable without internet connectivity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5674">Na ta način lahko izračunate natančno število sej za naše meritve v različnih rezinah strank (na najemnika, na sektor).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5674">This allows us to calculate an accurate session count for our metrics across slices of customers (per-tenant, per-sector).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5675">Prav tako lahko z njim filtrirate poročila o napakah, saj so na voljo številne napake pri sinhronizaciji, za katere pričakujemo, da bodo prišlo brez povezljivosti z omrežjem, vendar je to naloga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5675">We also use it to filter error reports as there are numerous sync errors that we expect to occur without network connectivity but that warrant investigation otherwise.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5676">Če teh podatkov ne prejmemo, ne bomo imeli natančnega nadzora nad delovanjem naših izdelkov ali ugotovili, ali pričakujete, da bo prišlo do napak, ki jih je izkusil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5676">If we do not receive this data, we will not be able to accurately monitor our products performance or determine if errors experienced by a user are expected or require further investigation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5677">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5677">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5678">**InternetConnectivityNowAvailable** – če je stanje povezljivosti spremenjeno, tako da je zdaj Internet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5678">**InternetConnectivityNowAvailable** -  If the connectivity state has been changed so it is now Internet</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragelegacyinboundlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5679">OneNote.Storage.LegacyInboundLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5679">OneNote.Storage.LegacyInboundLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5680">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja za spremljanje delovanja dohodnih postopkov sinhronizacije, ki neposredno komunicirajo s SharePointovim paketom, vključno s korelacijo podatkov, ki nam omogočajo nadzor in preiskovanje delovanja prenosa podatkov v našo storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5680">The critical signal used to track the performance of inbound sync operations that communicate directly with SharePoint including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5681">Ta signal je namenjen le najslabšem izvajanju prenosa v zadnjih 300 sekundah (število sekund, ki jih je mogoče konfigurirati z Microsoftom, odvisno od zmogljivosti in stanja storitve).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5681">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5685">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5685">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5686">**IsEducationNotebook** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je zvezek izobraževalni zvezek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5686">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5687">**NotebookId** – ID zvezka, v katerem je ta prenos vključen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5687">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5688">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** – čas v milisekundah, v katerem je bilo izvedeno nalaganje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5688">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload</span></span>
