<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5692">To se uporablja za zagotavljanje stanja storitev tako, da nam omogoči, da si ogledate, kateri najemniki doživljajo nesprejemljivo počasno dohodno podatkov za našo storitev, informacije o podatkih, ki jih prenašajo, ko so doživeli počasno dohodno in kako razširjena je v najemniku, ki je imel težave z zakasnitvijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5692">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow outbound of data to our service, information about the data they were uploading when they experienced the slow outbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5693">Uporablja se tudi za poročanje o stanju storitve in učinkovitosti delovanja v vseh naših strankah, s katerimi lahko izmerite trende v času in opozorite na težave, ki se samodejno uporabljajo za ublažitev strojništva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5693">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5694">Če teh podatkov ne bomo imeli, nam to prepreči, da bi zagotovili ustrezno učinkovitost delovanja, ko bodo uporabniki sinhronizirali spremembe v SharePointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5694">If we do not have this data, it will prevent us from ensuring adequate performance when syncing users changes up to SharePoint.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5695">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5695">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5696">**IsEducationNotebook** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je zvezek izobraževalni zvezek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5696">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5697">**NotebookId** – ID zvezka, v katerem je ta prenos vključen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5697">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5698">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** – čas v milisekundah, v katerem je bilo izvedeno nalaganje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5698">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimefiledataobjectdownload"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5699">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.FileDataObjectDownload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5699">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.FileDataObjectDownload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5700">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja za spremljanje učinkovitosti delovanja, ko uporabnik usmeri podatkovna datoteka (tj. vdelana datoteka ali slika), ki je prenesena neposredno iz naše storitve, in ne kot del operacije sinhroniziranja na strani, odseku ali zvezku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5700">The critical signal used to track performance when a user inbounds a file data object (i.e. an embedded file or image) which is downloaded directly from our service and not as part of a sync operation on a page, section or notebook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5701">Ta signal je namenjen le najslabšem izvajanju prenosa v zadnjih 300 sekundah (število sekund, ki jih je mogoče konfigurirati z Microsoftom, odvisno od zmogljivosti in stanja storitve).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5701">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5702">To se uporablja za zagotavljanje stanja storitve in zmogljivosti, tako da si lahko ogledate, kateri najemniki so nesprejemljivo počasna prenos podatkov iz naših storitev, in kako razširjena je v najemniku, ki je težava z zakasnitvijo, ter poroča o našem delu v določenem časovnem obdobju in nam tako omogoči, da merimo trende učinkovitosti delovanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5702">This is used to ensure service health and performance by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow download of data from our service, and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is, and report our behavior over time allowing us to measure service performance trends.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5703">Če opazite nesprejemljivo zakasnitev za predmet datoteke, bomo te podatke uporabili tudi za to, da bodo lahko sodelovali z drugimi signali iz odjemalca in storitve glede predmeta, ki bodo izboljšali postopek prenosa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5703">If we see an unacceptable latency for a file object, we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the object to make improvements to our download process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5704">Podatke smo razdelili tudi na podlagi razširitve predmeta datoteke, saj imamo različna pričakovanja glede na to, ali je datoteka predstavljena v vrstici z našim platnom (npr. slika) ali pa je datoteka, ki ni v vrstici (kot je besedilni dokument).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5704">We also split the data based on the extension of the file object downloaded as we have different expectations based on whether the file is presented inline in our canvas (e.g. an image) or is a non-inline file (such as a text document).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5705">Če teh podatkov ne prejmemo, nam prepreči nadzor učinkovitosti teh prenosov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5705">If we do not receive this data, it will prevent us from monitoring the performance of these downloads</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5706">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5706">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5707">**FileSizeInBytes** – velikost datoteke, ki jo prenesete v bajtih</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5707">**FileSizeInBytes** - The size of the file being downloaded in bytes</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5708">**IsImage** – logična vrednost, ki določa, ali je datoteka, ki jo prenesete, pripona, ki se ujema z vnaprej določenim seznamom pogostih oblik zapisa slike (.bmp, .emf, gif, .jpe, jpeg, jpg, png), ki je prikazana v vrstici v platnu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5708">**IsImage** - A bool determining if the file being downloaded has an extension that matches a pre-determined list of common image formats (.bmp, .emf, .gif, .jpe, .jpeg, .jpg, .png) that we display inline in the canvas</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5709">**TimeToDownload** – koliko časa je trajalo, da je FDO uspešno prenesla iz shrambe BLOB v napravo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5709">**TimeToDownload** - The length of time it took to successfully download the FDO from our blob storage to the device</span></span> 

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimewebsocketdownload"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5710">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketDownload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5710">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketDownload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5711">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja za spremljanje delovanja dohodnih sinhronizacijskih operacij, vključno s korelacijo podatkov, ki nam omogočajo nadzor in preiskovanje delovanja prenosa podatkov iz naših storitev (onenote.com).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5711">The critical signal used to track performance of inbound sync operations including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of downloading data from our service (onenote.com).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5712">Ta signal je namenjen le najslabšem izvajanju prenosa v zadnjih 300 sekundah (število sekund, ki jih je mogoče konfigurirati z Microsoftom, odvisno od zmogljivosti in stanja storitve).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5712">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5713">To se uporablja za zagotavljanje stanja storitev tako, da nam omogoči, da si ogledate, kateri najemniki doživljajo nesprejemljivo počasno dohodno podatkov za našo storitev, informacije o podatkih, ki jih prenašajo, ko so doživeli počasno dohodno in kako razširjena je v najemniku, ki je imel težave z zakasnitvijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5713">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow inbound of data from our service, information about the data they were downloading when they experienced the slow inbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5714">Uporablja se tudi za poročanje o stanju storitve in učinkovitosti delovanja v vseh naših strankah, s katerimi lahko izmerite trende v času in opozorite na težave, ki se samodejno uporabljajo za ublažitev strojništva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5714">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5715">Če opazite nesprejemljivo zakasnitev za odsek ali zvezek, bomo te podatke uporabili tudi za to, da bodo lahko sodelovali z drugimi signali v odjemalcu in storitvi v zvezi z istim dokumentom, da bodo prepoznali regresivne zmogljivosti odjemalca, ki nam bodo omogočale Dostavitev bolj zmogljive storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5715">If we see an unacceptable latency for a section or notebook we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the same document to identify client side performance regressions allowing us to deliver a more performant service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5716">Če teh podatkov ne prejmemo, ne bomo mogli nadzorovati učinkovitosti delovanja tega vidika naših storitev ali pa bo vpliv neželenih sprememb, ki so na voljo, morda zaradi uporabe ali drugih dejavnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5716">If we do not receive this data, we will be unable to monitor the performance of this aspect of our service, or the impact of server side changes we may find necessary due to usage or other factors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5717">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5717">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5718">**DeviceSessionId** – ID seje naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5718">**DeviceSessionId** -  The ID of the device session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5719">**IsEducationNotebook** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je zvezek izobraževalni zvezek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5719">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5720">**IsHierarchyResource** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je vir hierarhični vir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5720">**IsHierarchyResource** - A bool indicating if the resource is a hierarchy resource</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5721">**NotebookId** – ID zvezka, v katerem je ta prenos vključen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5721">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5722">**ResourceId** – ID vira, ki ga nalagamo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5722">**ResourceId** - The ID of the resource that we are uploading</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5723">**SectionId** – ID odseka, za katerega je ta prenos vključen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5723">**SectionId** - The ID of the section that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5724">**ServerSessionId** – ID seje strežnika, ki je ta prenos del programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5724">**ServerSessionId** - The ID of the server session that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5725">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** – čas v milisekundah med uporabnikom, ki se premikajo do strani, in sklad replikacije, ki potrjuje, da je stran sinhronizirana s strežnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5725">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds between a user navigating to a page and the replication stack confirming that page is in sync with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5726">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** – čas v milisekundah med mehanizmom sinhronizacije, ki se začne z dohodno replikacijo strani, in s tem postopkom replikacije, ki je dosegel sinhronizacijo s stanjem strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5726">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - The time in milliseconds between the sync engine beginning inbound replication of a page and that replication operation reaching the in sync with the server state.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5736">**IsEducationNotebook** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je zvezek izobraževalni zvezek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5736">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5737">**IsHierarchyResource** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je vir hierarhični vir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5737">**IsHierarchyResource** - A bool indicating if the resource is a hierarchy resource</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5738">**IsWorstTime** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je čas rednega prenosa, ali najslabšega časa, ki smo ga videli v tem odjemalcu v zadnjih 300 sekundah (število sekund je mogoče konfigurirati z Microsoftom, odvisno od učinkovitosti delovanja in pogoja storitve).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5738">**IsWorstTime** - A bool indicating if the time is a regular upload event, or the worst time we saw on this client in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5739">**NotebookId** – ID zvezka, v katerem je ta prenos vključen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5739">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5740">**RecommendedPutIntervalInMs** – čas, ko je storitev posredovana odjemalcu, kot je priporočeno obdobje »vstavi«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5740">**RecommendedPutIntervalInMs** - The time the service has communicated to the client as its recommended put interval</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5741">**ResourceId** – ID vira, ki ga nalagamo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5741">**ResourceId** - The ID of the resource that we are uploading</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5742">**SectionId** – ID odseka, za katerega je ta prenos vključen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5742">**SectionId** - The ID of the section that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5743">**SenderRequestId** – ID pošiljatelja, ki izvaja prenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5743">**SenderRequestId** - The ID of the sender performing the upload</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5744">**ServerSessionId** – ID seje strežnika, ki je ta prenos del programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5744">**ServerSessionId** - The ID of the server session that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5745">**UploadNonSuspendedTimeInMs** – čas v milisekundah, v katerem je bilo izvedeno nalaganje, razen časa, ko je bila aplikacija prekinjena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5745">**UploadNonSuspendedTimeInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload excluding the time when the application was suspended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5746">**UploadTimeInMs** – čas v milisekundah, v katerem je bilo dejansko izvedeno nalaganje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5746">**UploadTimeInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to actually perform the upload</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5747">**WaitTimeInMs** – čas v milisekundah med zahtevano nalaganje in prenosom, ki se začne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5747">**WaitTimeInMs** - The time in millseconds between an upload being requested and an upload starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5748">**WebUrl** – WebUrl prenosa (prijavljeno kot PiiWz)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5748">**WebUrl** - The WebUrl of the upload (Logged as a PiiWz)</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragesynchealth"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5749">OneNote.Storage.SyncHealth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5749">OneNote.Storage.SyncHealth</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5750">Kritični signal, s katerim lahko spremljate napake in izjeme, ki so se zgodile znotraj sklada za sinhronizacijo v odjemalcu za OneNote, s katerim lahko nadzorujete in omilimo te nepričakovane pogoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5750">The critical signal used to track errors and exceptions that have occurred inside the sync stack in the OneNote client allowing us to monitor and mitigate these unexpected conditions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5751">To se uporablja za zagotavljanje stanja storitev tako, da si lahko ogledate poročila o napakah odjemalcev, ki so na voljo v realnem času, kar nam omogoča odziv na težave pri sinhronizaciji, ko se pojavijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5751">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see error reports from the clients in near real-time, which lets us respond to sync issues as they arise.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5752">Uporablja se tudi za določanje, kako razširjena je težava, in kako huda je navzkrižna referenca z oznako napake z odjemalčevo kodo, da prepoznate izvor napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5752">It is also used to identify how widespread an issue is, and how severe by cross-referencing the error tag with the client code to identify the source of failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5753">Te podatke združimo tudi tako, da dobimo informacije o učinkovitosti delovanja skozi čas ter vpliva in učinkovitosti izboljšav, ki jih naredimo našim strankam in storitvam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5753">We also aggregate this data to get information on our performance over time and the impact and effectiveness of improvements we make to our clients and services.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5754">Če teh podatkov nimamo, ne bomo mogli proaktivno odgovoriti na pogoje napake v naši sinhronizacijski storitvi, ne da bi se med seboj stopnjevala stranka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5754">If we do not have this data, we won’t be able to proactively respond to error conditions in our sync service without customer escalation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5755">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5755">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5756">**Storitev** – storitev sinhronizacije, ki jo je stranka uporabljala, ko je prišlo do napake (podedovana ali sodobna sinhronizacija)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5756">**Service** - The sync service the client was using when the error occurred (Legacy or Modern Sync)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5757">**Oznaka** – oznaka (prepoznavna vrednost), ki predstavlja napako, ki jo je stranka naletela med postopkom sinhronizacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5757">**Tag** - The tag (a identifying value) representing the error that the client encountered during the sync operation</span></span>

### <a name="onenotesynccreatenotebookfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5758">OneNote.Sync.CreateNotebookFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5758">OneNote.Sync.CreateNotebookFailed</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5759">Ta dogodek se zabeleži, ko ustvarjanje zvezka ne uspe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5759">This event is logged when creation of a notebook fails.</span></span>  
 
<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5760">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5760">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5761">**NetworkConnection** – prijavi vrsto povezave, ki jo trenutno uporablja naprava, npr. Wi-Fi, brez povezave, 3G</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5761">**NetworkConnection** - Logs the connection type that the device is currently on e.g. Wi-Fi, offline, 3G</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5762">**ServerType** – prijavi vrsto strežnika, kjer naj bo ustvarjen zvezek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5762">**ServerType** - Logs the server type where notebook was to be created.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5767">**NetworkConnection** – prijavi vrsto povezave, ki jo trenutno uporablja naprava, npr. Wi-Fi, brez povezave, 3G</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5767">**NetworkConnection** - Logs the connection type that the device is currently on e.g. Wi-Fi, offline, 3G</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5768">**ServerType** – prijavi vrsto strežnika, v kateri je ustvarjen zvezek za hitri zapiske.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5768">**ServerType** - Logs the server type where Quick Notes notebook was to be created</span></span>

### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_telemetryoptin"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5772">Office_FirstRun_Apple_TelemetryOptIn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5772">Office_FirstRun_Apple_TelemetryOptIn</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5773">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5773">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5774">Ta dogodek se uporablja za nadzor stanja pretoka telemetrije, ki ste ga dovolili, pri izkušnji prvega zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5774">The event is used to monitor the health of our telemetry opt-in flow in First Run Experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5775">Zbiramo kodo, ki označuje vrsto možnosti zbirke diagnostičnih podatkov, ki jo je izbral uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5775">We collect a code that denotes what type of diagnostic data collection option was selected by the user.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5776">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5776">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5777">**Data_EventId** – koda, ki označuje nastavitve za diagnostično zbirko podatkov, ki jo je izbral uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5777">**Data_EventId** – A code indicating the diagnostic data collection preference selected by the user.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemgracefulexitgracefulappexitdesktop"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5778">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5778">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5779">Dogodek sproži elegantna zaustavitev aplikacije v primeru Officeovih odjemalskih aplikacij, kot so med drugim Word, Excel, PowerPoint in Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5779">The event is triggered by a graceful application termination for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5780">Z elegantno zaustavitvijo merimo stanje Officeovih odjemalcev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5780">We use Graceful Exit to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5781">Gre za ključni poslovni signal, ki ga Officeovi inženirji uporabljajo za zagotavljanje stabilnosti izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5781">It is intended to be a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5782">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5782">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5783">**AppBuild** – identifikator delovne različice za vplivani proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5783">**AppBuild** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5784">**AppMajor** – identifikator glavne različice za vplivani proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5784">**AppMajor** - Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5785">**AppMinor** – identifikator manjše različice za vplivani proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5785">**AppMinor** - Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5786">**AppRevision** – identifikator delovne različice za vplivani proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5786">**AppRevision** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5787">**BootCompleted** – ali je Officeov postopek dokončal zagon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5787">**BootCompleted** – Did Office process complete boot.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5788">**DetectionTime** – čas, ko je bil zaznan nepričakovani izhod.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5788">**DetectionTime** - The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5789">**EcsETag** – identifikator preskusa za proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5789">**EcsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5790">**HasEdit** – ali je bilo med Officeovim postopkom v teku urejanje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5790">**HasEdit** – Was document editing occurring during the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5791">**HasOpen** – ali je bil dokument odprt med Officeovim postopkom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5791">**HasOpen** – Was document opened during the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5792">**InstallMethod** – ali je bila trenutna gradnja Officea nadgrajena iz, povrnjena v prejšnje stanje oziroma sveža namestitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5792">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from, rolled back to, or a fresh install.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5793">**OfficeUILang** – jezik Officeovega postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5793">**OfficeUILang** – Language of the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5794">**PreviousBuild** – prejšnja nameščena delovna različica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5794">**PreviousBuild** - Previously installed build version.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5795">**SafeMode** – ali je bil Officeov postopek v varnem načinu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5795">**SafeMode** – Was Office process in safe mode.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5796">**SessionId** – enolični identifikator postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5796">**SessionId** - A unique identifier of the process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5797">**SessionInitTime** – čas, ko se je začel vplivani proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5797">**SessionInitTime** - The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemidentitychanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5798">Office.System.IdentityChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5798">Office.System.IdentityChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5799">Podatki o identiteti uporabnika, zahtevani za izpolnjevanje zahtev za zahtevo podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5799">User identity information required to fulfill data subject requests.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5800">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5800">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5801">**IdentityChanged** – ima vedno vrednost »True«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5801">**IdentityChanged** - Always true.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5802">Identiteta se je spremenila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5802">The identity changed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5803">**TimerDetectedChange** – ali je spremembo zaznal časovno usklajeni ping</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5803">**TimerDetectedChange** - Whether the change was detected by regularly timed ping.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemprivacyfallbacktosettingsstore"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5804">Office.System.PrivacyFallbackToSettingsStore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5804">Office.System.PrivacyFallbackToSettingsStore</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5805">Se uporablja za določanje, ali je prišlo do napak pri branju nastavitev zasebnosti uporabnika iz gostujoče shrambe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5805">Used to determine if there are failures with reading the user's privacy settings from the Roaming store.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5806">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5806">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5807">**Oznaka –** oznaka kode, ki ponazarja, katera nastavitev je bila podana nazaj v shrambo nastavitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5807">**Tag -** The code tag indicating which setting has fallen back to the settings store.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemsessiondatao365"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-5808">Office.System.SessionDataO365</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5808">Office.System.SessionDataO365</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5809">Metapodatki, zahtevani za osamitev ponovnega prikaza napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5809">Metadata required to isolate a failure reproduction.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-5810">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5810">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5811">**AppId** – identifikator, na katerega se nanašajo ti podatki Officeove aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5811">**AppId -** Identifier for what Office application this data refers to.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5812">**ApplicationArchitecture** – za katero arhitekturo procesorja je zgrajen Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5812">**ApplicationArchitecture -** What processor architecture Office is built for.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5813">**AppVersionBuild** – delovna različica Officeove aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5813">**AppVersionBuild -** The Build version of the Office application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5814">**AppVersionMajor** – glavna različica Officeove aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5814">**AppVersionMajor -** The Major version of the Office application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5815">**AppVersionMinor** – manjša različica Officeove aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5815">**AppVersionMinor -** The Minor version of the Office application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5816">**AppVersionUpdate** – delovna revizija Officeove aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5816">**AppVersionUpdate -** The Build Revision of the Office application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5817">**CollectorVersion** – identifikator različice za način zbiranja odjemalca</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5817">**CollectorVersion -** A version identifier for the client collection logic.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5818">**DeviceHash** – enosmerno zgoščevanje identifikatorja za operacijski sistem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5818">**DeviceHash -** A one-way hash of the operating system device identifier.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-5819">**DeviceName** ime naprave, v kateri je nameščen Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-5819">**DeviceName -** Name of the Device Office is run on.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6214">**UAETypeName** – identifikator razdeljevanja za način nenavadnega izhoda iz aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6214">**UAETypeName -** Bucketing identifier for how the app exited ungracefully.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6215">**VerifyElseCrashTag** – enolični identifikator za mesto zrušitve aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6215">**VerifyElseCrashTag -** Unique identifier for where the app crashed.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemsystemhealthungracefulapplicationexitwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-6245">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulApplicationExitWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6245">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulApplicationExitWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-6246">Dogodek sproži neobičajna prekinitev aplikacije (na primer prekinitev izvajanja upravitelja opravil, neodzivnost aplikacije ipd.) v primeru Officeovih odjemalskih aplikacij, kot so med drugim Word, Excel, PowerPoint in Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6246">The event is triggers by an abnormal application termination (for example, task manager kill, application hang, etc.) for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6247">Metriko motenega zapiranja aplikacij uporabljamo za merjenje stanja Officeovih odjemalskih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6247">We use Ungraceful Application Exit metrics to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6248">Gre za ključni poslovni signal, ki ga Officeovi inženirji uporabljajo za zagotavljanje stabilnosti izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6248">It is a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-6249">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6249">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6250">**AddinExecution –** zastavica, ki sporoča, ali se je dodatek izvajal in se med nenavadnim izhodom iz aplikacije ni končal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6250">**AddinExecution -** Flag that informs if an add-in was executing and didn't finish during an ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6251">**BootCompleted –** zagon Officea je bil ob trenutku zrušitve dokončan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6251">**BootCompleted –** Was Office boot completed at the time of crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6252">**CrashedProcessAppBuild** – identifikator delovne različice za vplivani proces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6252">**CrashedAppBuild -** Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6253">**CrashedAppMajor** – identifikator glavne različice za vplivani proces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6253">**CrashedAppMajor -** Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6254">**CrashedAppMinor** – identifikator manjše različice za vplivani proces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6254">**CrashedAppMinor -** Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6255">**CrashedAppRevision** – identifikator delovne različice za vplivani proces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6255">**CrashedAppRevision -** Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6256">**CrashedEcsETag** – identifikator preskusa za proces zrušitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6256">**CrashedEcsETag -** An experiment identifier for the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6257">**CrashedModuleName** – ime modula z napako</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6257">**CrashedModuleName -** Failing module name.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6258">**CrashedSessionID** – enolični identifikator procesa zrušitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6258">**CrashedSessionId -** A unique identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6259">**CrashedSessionInitTime** – čas, ko se je začel vplivani proces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6259">**CrashedSessionInitTime -** The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6260">**CrashTime –** ura, ki označuje, da odjemalec ni bil zaustavljen pravilno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6260">**CrashTime –** The time indicating the client terminated ungracefully.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6261">**CrashType** – identifikator razdeljevanja za vrsto zrušitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6261">**CrashType -** Bucketing identifier for the type of crash.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-6289">Dogodek se uporablja za metrike zrušitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6289">Used to capture crash metrics.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6294">**AppName** – ime vplivane aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6294">**AppName -** The name of the affected application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6295">**AppRevisionVersion** – identifikator revizije delovne različice za vplivani proces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6295">**AppRevisionVersion -** Build revision identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6297">**CrashedConfigIds** – konfiguracija, dodeljena procesu zrušitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6297">**CrashedConfigIds -** The configuration assigned to the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6298">**CrashedImpressionId** – identifikator vtisa za proces zrušitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6298">**CrashedImpressionId -** The impression identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6299">**CrashedInteractionSessionId** – identifikator seje interakcije za proces rušitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6299">**CrashedInteractionSessionId -** The interaction session identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6300">**CrashedProcessSessionID** – enolični identifikator procesa zrušitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6300">**CrashedProcessSessionId -** A unique identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6301">**CrashType** – identifikator razdeljevanja za vrsto zrušitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6301">**CrashType -** Bucketing identifier for the type of crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6302">**ErrorString** – opis napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6302">**ErrorString -** Error description.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6303">**ExceptionAddress** – mesto v programu, kjer je prišlo do napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6303">**ExceptionAddress -** Address in the program where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6304">**ExceptionCode** – identifikator razdeljevanja za izjemo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6304">**ExceptionCode -** Bucketing identifier for the exception.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6305">**FaultAppName** – ime aplikacije z napako</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6305">**FaultAppName -** The name of the faulting app.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6306">**InstallMethod** – ali je bila trenutna gradnja Officea nadgrajena iz, povrnjena v prejšnje stanje oziroma sveža namestitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6306">**InstallMethod -** Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from, rolled back to, or a fresh install.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6307">**InstallType** – identifikator za način namestitve Officea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6307">**InstallType -** An identifier for the method by which Office was installed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6308">**IsDebug** – ali je to gradnja Officea za odpravljanje napak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6308">**IsDebug -** Whether this is a debug build of Office.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6309">**IsHandledCrash** – ali je bil program za obravnavno rušitve pozvan v seji zrušitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6309">**IsHandledCrash -** Whether the crash handler was invoked in the crashing session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6310">**IsLabMachine** – ali se Office izvaja v Microsoftovem laboratoriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6310">**IsLabMachine -** Whether Office is being run in a Microsoft lab.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6311">**ModuleBaseAddress** – osnovni naslov modula z napako</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6311">**ModuleBaseAddress -** Base Address of the failing module.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6312">**ModuleName** – ime modula z napako</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6312">**ModuleName -** Failing module name.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6313">**ModuleOffset** – odmik v bajtih od osnovnega mesta, kjer je prišlo do napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6313">**ModuleOffset -** Offset in bytes from the base address where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6314">**ModuleSize** – velikost modula z napako v bajtih</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6314">**ModuleSize -** Failing module size in bytes.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6315">**OSEnvironment** – identifikator za okolje, v katerem se izvaja Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6315">**OSEnvironment -** Identifier for what environment Office is running on.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6316">**PreviousBuild** – prejšnja nameščena delovna različica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6316">**PreviousBuild -** Previously installed build version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6317">**PreviousInteractionSessionTime** – čas, ko je bila zagnana seja prejšnje interakcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6317">**PreviousInteractionSessionTime -** Time which the previous interaction session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6318">**PreviousLifecycleState** – identifikator stanja življenjskega cikla za prejšnjo sejo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6318">**PreviousLifecycleState -** Previous session lifecycle state identifier.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6319">**PreviousSessionInitTime** – čas, ko je bila zagnana prejšnja seja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6319">**PreviousSessionInitTime -** Time when the previous session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6320">**StackHash** – identifikator, ki ponazarja mesto v kodi, kjer je prišlo do zrušitve vplivanega procesa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6320">**StackHash -** An identifier indicating where in code that the affected process crashed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6321">**VerifyElseCrashTag** – enolični identifikator za mesto zrušitve aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6321">**VerifyElseCrashTag -** Unique identifier for where the app crashed.</span></span>

### <a name="officetelemetryvolumetrackingdata"></a><span data-ttu-id="4312e-6602">Office.Telemetry.VolumeTrackingData</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6602">Office.Telemetry.VolumeTrackingData</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-6603">Metrika za sledenje količine dogodkov za dogodke telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6603">Event volume tracking metrics for telemetry events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4312e-6604">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6604">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6605">**EventThreshold** – največje število primerkov za posamezen dogodek, ki ga lahko pošljete v časovnem oknu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6605">**EventThreshold** - The maximum number of instances of a single event that can be sent in a window of time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6606">**HighestEventCount** – najvišje število primerkov za posamezen dogodek, poslan v tem oknu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6606">**HighestEventCount** - The highest number of instances of a single event sent this window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6607">**HighestEventName** – ime dogodka z najvišjim številom primerkov v tem oknu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6607">**HighestEventName** - The name of the event with the highest number of instances in this window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6608">**TimeWindowInSeconds** – trajanje okna v sekundah</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6608">**TimeWindowInSeconds** - The duration of the window in seconds.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6609">**TotalEvents** – skupno število dogodkov, poslanih v oknu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6609">**TotalEvents** - The total number of events sent during the window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="4312e-6610">**UniqueEvents** – število enoličnih dogodkov, poslanih v oknu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4312e-6610">**UniqueEvents** - The number of unique events sent during a window.</span></span>
